Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.39,0:00:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[Man ]...to recover contents such as shoes, socks and undergarments.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.89,0:00:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}现在播报特别报导{\r}\NAnd now an item of special note.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.76,0:00:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在变幻多端的气候下{\r}\NBarring any change in the weather,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.50,0:00:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}片名：早安越南 133军团和第4步兵团手球赛{\r}\Nthe softball game between the 133rd and 4th infantry divisions...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.47,0:00:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}将在班米都公园举行{\r}\Nwill resume as scheduled at the Ban Mi Thout Park,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.27,0:00:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}叶何转角处，西贡的文班秋街{\r}\Ncorner of Viet Ho and Hguen Van Theiuh streets here in Saigon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.57,0:00:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}请密切注意{\r}\NPlease make a note of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.41,0:00:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对不起{\r}\N[ Clears Throat ] Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.74,0:00:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}上周在大雨中遗失装备的人员{\r}\NThose men who lost equipment in last week's rains...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.18,0:00:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}请与山母.谢尔中尉连络{\r}\Nare asked to contact Lieutenant Sam Scheer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.88,0:00:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}史纳尔中尉...{\r}\NLieutenant Schneer--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.98,0:00:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谢尔中尉要求大家{\r}\N Lieutenant Scheer asks those men with waterlogged mitts...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.55,0:00:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在申请新装备前尽量在水中寻找{\r}\Nto make every effort to dry them out in the sun before requesting new ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.32,0:01:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}书虫！西贡总部支援的图书馆{\r}\NBookworms, Headquarters Support Activities Saigon...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.49,0:01:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}分设于6个地点{\r}\Noperates libraries at six locations in the Republic of Vietnam.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.60,0:01:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}美国人员能在古拜，迪南，方涛{\r}\NAmerican personnel can check out a book in Ku Bai, Da Nang,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}西贡，边化和山泉借到书{\r}\NPhung Tao, Saigon, Bien Wah and San Treng.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.87,0:01:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如你无法亲自去挑选书籍{\r}\NIf you can't stop in and select your own books,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.37,0:01:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}写信给HSAS图书馆{\r}\Nwrite to the H.S.A.S. Library.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.47,0:01:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}写明作者，书名，主题{\r}\NAsk for the books by author, title and subject,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.14,0:01:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你所选的书将会邮寄给你{\r}\Nand your selections will be mailed to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.21,0:01:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}假日已渐渐接近{\r}\NWith the holiday season rapidly approaching,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.58,0:01:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那些将发圣诞卡回家的人...{\r}\Nthose personnel wishing to spend Christmas cards home--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.79,0:01:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}希望寄圣诞卡回家的人{\r}\Nwishing to send Christmas cards home to the States--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.62,0:01:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}请在10月13日前寄出{\r}\Nare asked to do so no later than August 13,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.56,0:01:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}因在那之后邮件将会大增...{\r}\Ndue to a yearly mail rush at that time. - Don't disappoint your-- - [ Loud Static ]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.27,0:01:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So take your liberties, but watch the liberties you take.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.84,0:01:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lost luggage:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.45,0:02:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}陆军部对于物品在运送途中遗失{\r}\Nthe Armed Forces sincerely regrets any inconvenience...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.22,0:02:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}所引起的不方便感到十分抱歉{\r}\Ndue to luggage lost on transport carriers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.52,0:02:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}单人遗失的物品...{\r}\NPersonal missing luggage-- 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.42,0:02:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}应该是个人遗失的物品的人{\r}\Nthat should be personnel missing luggage--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.16,0:02:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}请在5日前寄张卡片至克少校处{\r}\Nare asked to drop a card to Major Gerald Kleiner over at the Fifth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.26,0:02:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}卡片不要超过4X5寸大小{\r}\NThe card should be no larger than four by five inches...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.93,0:02:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}并请说明物品内的东西{\r}\Nand should describe the contents of your duffel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.00,0:02:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}克少校希望大家 克少校希望大家{\r}\Nand should describe the contents of your duffel. Major Kleiner requests that you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.93,0:02:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不要描述物品的外形{\r}\Ndo not describe your duffel
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.74,0:02:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}因所有的物品看来都差不多{\r}\Nas all duffels look alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.97,0:02:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}遗失物品的人员...{\r}\NThose personnel with lost bag--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.81,0:02:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- All right. - Hey, Sarge, where are the women?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.68,0:02:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}康纳空军人员？{\r}\N- Airman Cronauer?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.65,0:02:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没错{\r}\N- You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.39,0:02:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}欢迎到西贡来，长官{\r}\N[ Chuckles ] Welcome to Saigon, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.62,0:02:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}小心点，你可能会刺到眼睛{\r}\N- Careful. You could put an eye out with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.22,0:02:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}很暖和吧！{\r}\N- God, it's warm, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.32,0:02:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}暖和？不是{\r}\NWarm? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如是在伦敦的话早就晒死人了{\r}\N This is a setting for London broil.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.53,0:02:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我是艾德.蒙特秋.加利上士{\r}\NI'm Private First Class Edward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.70,0:02:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}听你差遣，长官{\r}\NMontesque Garlick at your service, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.80,0:02:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你第一件事就是去改个新名字{\r}\NFirst thing, Garlick, is you gotta requisition a new name.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.10,0:02:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我已喜欢你了{\r}\N[ Giggles ] I like you already, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.20,0:02:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}事实上我是你在西贡军中电台{\r}\NActually, what I am, sir, is your Armed Forces Radio Saigon assistant who's in charge...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.21,0:03:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}负责协调和人事上的助理{\r}\Nof orientation and billeting of enlisted personnel, 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.28,0:03:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}以及电台职员{\r}\Nand company clerk. Whew.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.75,0:03:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我很感动{\r}\NI'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.58,0:03:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}已经发动了{\r}\N- # # [ Perry Como On Radio ] - It's already started.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.15,0:03:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我了解{\r}\N- I understand. - [ Nervous Giggle ]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dream on
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.50,0:03:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Little dreamer Dream on
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.80,0:03:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dream about a love so fine
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.04,0:03:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet as apple berry wine
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.51,0:03:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dream on
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.95,0:03:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Little dreamer Dream on
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.32,0:03:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这是西贡AFRS电台{\r}\N- [ Horns Honking ] - [ Man On Radio ] This is AFRS, Radio Saigon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.03,0:03:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}AFRS电台是隶属美国政府{\r}\NAFRS Radio is owned and operated by the United States government... and operates on an assigned carrier frequency of 540...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.10,0:04:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这小子像鲸鱼粪一样无聊{\r}\N- at 7 49 megahertz. - Jesus, that guy's as boring as whale shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不尽然，这是宣布广播的途径{\r}\N- And now AFRS is proud to bring you the following... - Not really. See, the purpose is to inform you as to the radius of the radio waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.58,0:04:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}蒙特瓦尼？那是给失眠者{\r}\N- by Mantovani. - Mantovani?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.54,0:04:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在服了大量安眠药仍睡不着听的{\r}\NThey play Mantovani to insomniacs who don't respond to strong drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.65,0:04:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}将军喜欢轻音乐...{\r}\NThe general likes easy listening. I'm really gonna have to inform you--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.95,0:04:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}紧急事件！ 11点钟方向{\r}\NMayday! Mayday! Dragon lady with incredible figure at eleven o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.78,0:04:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有位身材极佳的龙女，停车{\r}\N- Stop the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.55,0:04:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我办不到，长官{\r}\N- I can't do that, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.59,0:04:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}为什么？我真不明白{\r}\NEdward, you don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.12,0:04:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}希腊有个小岛上女人有如女神般{\r}\NI've been on a Greek island with women who look like Zorba.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.69,0:04:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我以为再也找不到那样的小姐{\r}\NI never thought I'd find women attractive ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.56,0:04:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}现在找到了，你竟不停车？{\r}\NAnd now that I do, you won't even turn the car around?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.49,0:04:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}多谢了{\r}\N Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.56,0:04:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你和主管有重要的会议{\r}\N- You have a very important meeting with the top brass. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她又出现了，她怎么在我们前面 那是另外一个人{\r}\N- Oh! There she is again! How'd she get ahead of us? - That's another person, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.10,0:04:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她美丽，又快速{\r}\NAh, she's beautiful and quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.50,0:04:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}加油门，试试活力{\r}\NSpeed up. Check her stamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.74,0:04:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不可思议{\r}\NThis is incredible! My God, they're quick. They're fast and small.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我的天，她们又快又美又小 我觉得像是狐狸进了鸡窝了{\r}\NHa-ha-ha-ha! I feel like a fox in a chicken coop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.92,0:04:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们来了一位新进人员{\r}\NWe got a new man comin' in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.15,0:04:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}了解吗？迪克{\r}\N- Don't you understand, Dick?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.29,0:04:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不，长官，老实说我不了解{\r}\N- No, sir. Frankly, I do not understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.26,0:04:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}请你把音调放低点，好吗？{\r}\NWould you kindly lower your tone, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.33,0:05:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是{\r}\NYes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.46,0:05:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}节目都是我在掌理的，将军{\r}\NI run this show, General. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.27,0:05:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如有差错的话是我倒霉{\r}\NIf anything screws up, it's my ass in the morgue.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.70,0:05:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如有任何变动应该通知我{\r}\NI deserve to be notified of any changes that are made.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.30,0:05:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对于这桌没有人和你争执{\r}\NNobody's arguing that with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我在克圭岛听到这小子的节目{\r}\NLook, I caught his show on the lsle of Crete, and this guy is funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.08,0:05:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他很风趣，我差点笑死{\r}\NI damn near busted a gut laughing at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}部队爱死了{\r}\NAnd the troops, they love him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.28,0:05:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这只是小改变，根本不算什么{\r}\NThis is a tempest in a teacup, much ado about nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.75,0:05:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}天呀！这不是脑部手术{\r}\NFor crying out loud, man, this isn't brain surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.96,0:05:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别反应过度了，迪克{\r}\NDon't get crazy over this, Dick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.79,0:05:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们只是在谈一名鬼D. J而已{\r}\NWe're only talking about a damn deejay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.83,0:05:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}长官，在西贡已没有{\r}\NSir, there is no such thing as "only" anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}只有如此而已的事了{\r}\N Not now. Not in Saigon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.13,0:05:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}史帝芬.哈克中尉是直属长官{\r}\NLieutenant Steven Hauk is our immediate supervisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.54,0:05:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他有点古怪，但他人还不错{\r}\NHe's a little goofy, but he's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.97,0:05:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}迪克生士官长...{\r}\NSergeant Major Dickerson-- [ Laughs ]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.98,0:05:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那则完全是另一回事{\r}\NThat's another story altogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.91,0:05:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他是精选特种部队的小队长{\r}\NHe was a commander of an elite special forces unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.75,0:05:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}因神精质问题而调来这里{\r}\NHe came to us because of prostrate problems...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.92,0:05:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}某种社会影响性的问题无法解决{\r}\Nand some sort of social infection that doesn't go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.42,0:05:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}外加我认为他是屁股中弹{\r}\NPlus, I think he got shot in the ass, but I can't confirm that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.92,0:06:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但我无法确认这件事 总之，他是你不想去惹的人{\r}\N[ Giggling ] Anyway, he's the man that you don't want to aggravate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.29,0:06:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你一向这么快乐吗？{\r}\N- Ed, are you always this happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.73,0:06:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}康纳 长官{\r}\N- Cronauer!- Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.40,0:06:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}稍息，我是泰勒将军{\r}\N- At ease. I'm General Taylor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.37,0:06:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你好，将军{\r}\N- Hiya, General.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.37,0:06:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}幸会{\r}\N- A real pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.47,0:06:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你如果有问题的话只管来找我{\r}\NListen, if you have any problems here now, you come see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.37,0:06:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我是这里的最高长官{\r}\N- I'm the tallest hog in the trough around here. - [ Laughs ]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.34,0:06:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你又肥了吗？{\r}\N- Garlick, have you put on some weight?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.91,0:06:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想没有，长官{\r}\N- I don't think so, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.24,0:06:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}照你屁股的影子来看{\r}\NWhy, son, the shadow
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.78,0:06:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你像重了二十磅{\r}\Nof your ass'd weigh 20 pounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.02,0:06:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我会努力，长官{\r}\N- [ Chuckling ] - I'll work on that, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.42,0:06:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你不该对将军说你好{\r}\NYou're not supposed to address the general saying "hiya."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.69,0:06:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}又有新的规定吗？{\r}\N- What's that, a new rule?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.05,0:06:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不，老规定{\r}\N- No, an old rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.26,0:06:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}里面那位是哈克中尉{\r}\N- That's Lt. Hauk in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.66,0:06:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}大耳朵的那位是谁？{\r}\N- Who's the guy with the ears?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.66,0:06:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你好，他可以用那耳朵飞到关岛{\r}\NHow're you doin'? He could fly to Guam with those.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.40,0:06:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}空军人员康纳{\r}\NUh, Airman Cronauer, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.57,0:06:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}偶而向我敬个礼不会害死你们的{\r}\NYou know, i-it wouldn't kill you people to salute me once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}抱歉{\r}\N- Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.01,0:06:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谢谢{\r}\N- Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.58,0:06:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我知道你是位很风趣的D. J{\r}\NI understand you're pretty funny as a deejay,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.95,0:07:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}说笑话是我的一种喜好{\r}\Nand well, comedy is a kind of hobby of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}事实上，那不仅是一种喜好{\r}\NWell-- Well, actually, it's a little more than just a hobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.25,0:07:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}读者文摘考虑采用我的二则笑话{\r}\NReader's Digest is considering publishing two of my jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.89,0:07:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}真的？{\r}\N- Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.96,0:07:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对{\r}\N- Y eah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.43,0:07:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}也许那天晚上可以交换一下心得{\r}\NAnd perhaps some night we could maybe get together and swap humorous stories...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.13,0:07:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好玩的{\r}\N for fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.03,0:07:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有何不可？{\r}\NOh, why not? 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}也许再放几张厄尼.福特的唱片{\r}\NAnd maybe play a couple of Tennessee Ernie Ford records.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.53,0:07:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那才叫精彩！{\r}\N- That'd be a hoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.80,0:07:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那是笑话，对不？{\r}\N- That's a joke, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.84,0:07:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}也许{\r}\N- Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.57,0:07:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我听的明白{\r}\N- I get it. - Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.78,0:07:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这人的文件呢？{\r}\NWhere is this man's paperwork?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.12,0:07:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在这里，士官长{\r}\N- Right here, Sergeant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.65,0:07:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谢谢，长官{\r}\N- Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}美国空军，由帽子上认出来的{\r}\NUnited States Air Force. The hat does give you away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.47,0:07:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这不是军中所发的衣服{\r}\NThis is not military issue, Airman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这是那一种军服？{\r}\NWhat sort of uniform is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.67,0:07:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}海岛服装{\r}\NCretan camouflage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.97,0:07:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如你想和一群希腊酒鬼打成一片{\r}\NIf you want to blend into a crowd of drunken Greeks, 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.64,0:07:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这个最适合{\r}\Nthere's nothin' better.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.84,0:08:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那是幽默！{\r}\NThat is humor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.81,0:08:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我认的出来{\r}\NI recognize that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.55,0:08:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我也认的出来你是位军人{\r}\NI also recognize your species of soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.42,0:08:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有次我在战场上也有位你这种人{\r}\NI had a guy like you in the field one time. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.45,0:08:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他被炸成碎片，在他还未幽默前 害死了三位好军人{\r}\NHe blew himself to pieces. But not before his humor cost the lives of three very fine individuals.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.36,0:08:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我希望...  你给我住嘴{\r}\N- I hope-- - You shut your fuckin' hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你现在东南亚，你是在出任务{\r}\NYou're in Southeast Asia now, pal. You got your cushy little assignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.36,0:08:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对这点我是无能为力{\r}\NThere's nothing I can do about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.67,0:08:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}到时候，你会使我忘了这件事{\r}\NIn time, you will make me forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.80,0:08:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你别犯到我就不会有问题{\r}\NYou stay out of my way, there'll be no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.47,0:08:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但如你和我玩花样的话{\r}\NBut if you toy with me, I'll burn you so bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.21,0:08:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我会整到你希望在小孩时就死了{\r}\Nyou'll wish you died as a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.98,0:08:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我说的够清楚吗？{\r}\N- Am I being fairly clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.71,0:08:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是，长官  长官？{\r}\N- Yes, sir. "Sir"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.52,0:08:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我是以此维生的，空军{\r}\NI work for a living, Airman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你要叫我迪克生士官长{\r}\NYou will address me as Sgt. Major Dickerson.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.39,0:08:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是，迪克生士官长{\r}\NYes, Sgt. Major Dickerson.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.69,0:08:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他使我想起唐纳.里{\r}\NHe reminds me a lot of Donna Reed,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.06,0:08:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}特别是眼睛部份{\r}\Nespecially around the eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.53,0:08:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}哈，哈，哈{\r}\NHello, hello, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.23,0:09:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这是你们的诺亚上尉牧师{\r}\NThis is your chaplain, Captain Noel,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.17,0:09:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你们个人信仰的节目{\r}\Nyour radio program of personal beliefs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.17,0:09:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}今天伟大而多样化的祝福是{\r}\NGreat and manifold are our blessings today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.58,0:09:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这奇迹式的无线电使我有机会{\r}\NThis great godly miracle of radio... really gives me the opportunity...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.02,0:09:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}能在空中与你们讲话{\r}\Nto speak to you on the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.59,0:09:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}长官，该起床了{\r}\NSir, it's time to rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.42,0:09:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}天呀，这大麻真厉害，我还在飘{\r}\NMy God, it's Mardi Gras, and I'm on the main float.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.53,0:09:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}起床吧，长官{\r}\NCome on, sir. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.53,0:09:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}再过二周就会习惯了{\r}\NA couple of weeks, this will be easy for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.03,0:09:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}让我再睡{\r}\N- Oh, let me go back to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.16,0:09:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}该起床了{\r}\N- You gotta get up, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.97,0:09:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}几点了？艾德{\r}\NGod. What time is it, Edward?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.37,0:09:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}5点半{\r}\N- It's 5:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.04,0:09:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}5点半，还很早{\r}\N- 5:30. It's very early.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.70,0:09:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我也许要伤害你了， 5分后叫我{\r}\NI may have to hurt you. Call me in five minutes. Ohh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.27,0:09:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不，你要马上起床，你要去广播{\r}\NNo, you have to get up right now and you have to get on the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.91,0:09:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Oh. Fine. - Come on, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.94,0:09:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这边，走廊尽头右手边 对{\r}\N[ Man ]...has signed Les Crane to a late night talk show. This way, sir. It's just down the hall and to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.72,0:09:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你一定很紧张{\r}\N- You must be nervous, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.95,0:09:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我甚至还没清醒{\r}\N- I'm not even in my body, Edward.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.38,0:09:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}放心！一切会很顺利，这边{\r}\NDon't worry about it. It'll go great. This way, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.76,0:09:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}“在电视直播发布会上K”{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.63,0:10:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}“詹森总统宣布K”{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.40,0:10:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}“美国派驻越南的军队K”{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}“将很快从目前的73，000人”{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.04,0:10:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}“增至125，000人”{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.91,0:10:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}离节目开始你还有几分钟{\r}\NWe still have a few minutes before your show begins, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.68,0:10:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}当要播新闻时就从机器上撕下来{\r}\NWhen it's time to read the news, you just take it off these machines here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但是，对念的内容要注意{\r}\NBut regardless of what you read,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.98,0:10:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}国防部要先过滤{\r}\NAirman, the Department of Defense wants final say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.85,0:10:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}每条新闻都要经过这二位的检查{\r}\NSo every item's checked by these two guys in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.99,0:10:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}二位，见见新D. J ，康纳{\r}\NGuys, I'd like you to meet our new deejay, Adrian Cronauer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.98,0:10:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那是马帝.李.卓厄斯{\r}\N- [ Muffled Talking ] - That's Marty Lee Dreiwitz.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.22,0:10:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他有洁癖{\r}\NHe's impeccably clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.15,0:10:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他由威斯康辛运来清洁用品{\r}\NThis man has cleaning products shipped in from Wisconsin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.99,0:11:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他也是你的室友{\r}\NHe's also one of your roommates, 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.72,0:11:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我是你的话我会考虑去自杀{\r}\Nso if I were you, I'd think about suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.96,0:11:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}长官，我认为你别用那些唱片{\r}\NSir, l-I really don't think that you want to use any of those records, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.40,0:11:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们已挑选好了...{\r}\N- We have a selection right here that's prepared specifically-- - Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.47,0:11:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我一直期望见到你{\r}\NI've been looking forward to meeting you. Listen, could you do me a favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.23,0:11:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}能帮我个忙吗？能马上说笑话吗 我怀疑{\r}\N- Can you say something funny right this minute? - I doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.20,0:11:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我支持你，我和你同一国的{\r}\N[ Guffawing ] I'm with you, man. I'm on your frequency.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.14,0:11:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我问你一个问题{\r}\NLet me ask you a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.48,0:11:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}乔依.比许有什么专长？{\r}\NWhat is the appeal of Joey Bishop?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.98,0:11:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那人不风趣{\r}\NI mean, the man's not funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.21,0:11:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我知什么是风趣，他可不风趣{\r}\NI know funny, and he's not funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.38,0:11:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别误会我，他是好人{\r}\NDon't get me wrong. He seems like a nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.02,0:11:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我父亲也是好人，但他也不风趣{\r}\NBut my father's a nice guy and he's not funny either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.29,0:11:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我真希望有人能说明一下{\r}\NI wish someone would explain this one to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.79,0:11:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你还有十秒就要上节目了{\r}\NYou're on the air in about ten seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.66,0:11:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}9 ， 8 ， 7 ， 6...{\r}\NNine, eight, seven, six--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.70,0:11:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这是虚构与事实的马帝{\r}\NHey, this has been "Fiction and Fact" from Marty Lee's almanac.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}现在直接由希腊来的{\r}\NAnd now, direct from Crete,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.53,0:11:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}欢迎平滑如丝绢般的声音康纳！{\r}\Nwelcome the silky-smooth sound of Airman Adrian Cronauer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.54,0:11:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}早安，越南{\r}\N[ Loud ] Go-oo-ood morning, Vietnam!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.95,0:12:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这不是试音，这是摇滚乐{\r}\NHey, this is not a test. This is rock and roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.45,0:12:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}由代尔摇滚到DMZ{\r}\NTime to rock it from the delta to the D.M.Z.!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.99,0:12:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是我吗？还是像猫王的声音{\r}\NIs that me, or does that sound like an Elvis Presley movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.85,0:12:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,# Viva, Da Nang Oh, viva, Da Nang #
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.16,0:12:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,# Da Nang me, Da Nang me Why don't they get a rope and hang me #
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.39,0:12:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这么早是否太大声了，太迟了{\r}\NHey, is it a little too early for being that loud? Hey, too late.
