Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.95,0:18:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}为何？{\r}\NWhy is that? 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.69,0:18:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}因为你们全要去森林里，看不见{\r}\N"Because you go in the jungle, I can't see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.32,0:18:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}就像在铁笼里穿条子衣服{\r}\NIt's like wearing stripes and plaid. I want to do something different.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.76,0:18:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想改变一下，要去森林就声明{\r}\NYou go in the jungle, make a statement. If you're going to fight, clash.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.33,0:18:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如要去打仗，穿麻布袋，明白吗{\r}\N- You know what I mean?"" - # Come on, baby, The time is right #
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.63,0:18:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,# Love your daddy with all your might #
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谢谢这美妙的音乐{\r}\NThank you for that lovely tune.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.90,0:18:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那热门乡村曲会陪我们到天明{\r}\N That funky music will drive us 'til the dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.11,0:18:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}让我们跳舞到吐血为止{\r}\NLet's boogaloo 'til we puke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.04,0:18:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}艾德伦时间快到了{\r}\NThat's about it for the Adrian Cron Hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.98,0:18:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我要去坐上驾驶座上了{\r}\NI'm gonna take myself out of the driver's seat, but I'm gonna turn you over...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.71,0:18:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但我要转交给刺激先生... 一位头发稀疏的人，但是位火球{\r}\Nto Mr. Excitement, a man with limp, damaged hair, but nevertheless a fireball,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.55,0:18:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}丹.拉文登！{\r}\NDan Levitan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.16,0:18:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这是西贡AFRS电台{\r}\NThis is AFRS, Radio Saigon, and yours truly,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.13,0:18:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我是主持人丹.拉文登{\r}\NDan "The Man" Levitan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.13,0:19:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}向越南地区所有官员问好致敬{\r}\NGreetings and salutations to any and all servicemen in the area...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.97,0:19:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谢谢各位收听本台的节目{\r}\Nand thanks so much for joining us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.24,0:19:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他很风趣，我知道，这小子风趣{\r}\NY eah, he's funny! I know funny. This guy is funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.61,0:19:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Sensational!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.62,0:19:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}稍息！{\r}\N- At ease!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.22,0:19:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们已经是了{\r}\N- Hell, we already are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.99,0:19:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}少耍嘴皮子{\r}\NJust cool your tongue, Airman,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.36,0:19:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}因我要讨论一下你的节目{\r}\Nbecause I intend to take issue with your performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.89,0:19:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}首先，别开天气的玩笑{\r}\NFirst of all, don't make fun of the weather here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.93,0:19:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别说这里的天气都是一样的{\r}\NAnd don't say that the weather is the same all the time here,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.27,0:19:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}因为不是，事实上{\r}\Nbecause it's not.- In fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.00,0:19:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}今天比昨天要低二度{\r}\Nit's two degrees cooler today than yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.10,0:19:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}低二度？{\r}\N- Two degrees cooler?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.67,0:19:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我竟没穿皮大衣{\r}\N- [ Gasps ] Me without my muff. - [ Dreiwitz Guffawing ]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.47,0:19:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我在主持个会议{\r}\N- Muff! I tell you, this guy's funny. - I'm trying to run a meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.55,0:19:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}知道吗？{\r}\NYou know, 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.71,0:19:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我憎恨你们这些人从不对我敬礼{\r}\NI hate the fact that you people never salute me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.55,0:19:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我是中尉，我有时喜欢敬个礼{\r}\NI am a lieutenant, and I would like salutes occasionally.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.45,0:19:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}阶级比较高就是这么回事{\r}\NThat's what being a higher rank is all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.62,0:19:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}第二...{\r}\NSecond--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.29,0:19:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}第二...{\r}\N- Second-- - Programming taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.96,0:19:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}节目口味{\r}\NProgramming taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}老实说，我觉得你的警方行动{\r}\NFrankly, I found your "l love a police action" 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有点太离谱了{\r}\Nremark way out of line.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.33,0:20:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你怎能把越南和一杯咖啡并论呢{\r}\NHow can you have the gall to compare the conflict here in Vietnam... with a glass of cappuccino coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.97,0:20:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}就这样想出来，我只想风趣一下{\r}\NWell, I was-- It just comes up. I was trying to be funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.98,0:20:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}风趣很好{\r}\N- Funny is good. Funny is good. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.91,0:20:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但那是用在喜剧和幽默上的{\r}\NBut then do it by using comedy and humor,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.78,0:20:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不是在警方行动和咖啡上{\r}\Nnot police action and coffee remarks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.88,0:20:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}更进一步，你要播放正常的音乐{\r}\NFurthermore, you are to stick to playing normal modes of music,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.82,0:20:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不是狂野的东西{\r}\Nnot wild stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.19,0:20:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在这里能接受的包括{\r}\NThose we would find acceptable here would include Lawrence Welk,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.99,0:20:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}劳伦斯.华克，吉母.纳伯 蒙特瓦尼！  伯西.费斯{\r}\NJim Nabors, Mantovani.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.63,0:20:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}伯西.费斯，很好{\r}\N- Percy Faith. - Percy Faith. Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.50,0:20:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}安迪.威廉，派瑞.科摩{\r}\NAndy Williams, Perry Como and
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.74,0:20:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}和法兰克.辛纳屈的一些曲子{\r}\Ncertain ballads by Mr. Frank Sinatra.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.47,0:20:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}巴伯.迪伦也不行吗？{\r}\N- Would Bob Dylan be out of line? 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.74,0:20:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}绝对不行{\r}\NO- Way, way, way out of line. ut of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.91,0:20:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}前任副总统尼克森本周会来{\r}\N- Former V.P. Richard Nixon will arrive here this week. - [ Garlick Giggles ]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.88,0:20:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}卓威兹，我指派你负责P.C{\r}\NDreiwitz, I've assigned you to cover the P.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.05,0:20:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他喜欢把记者招待会说成P.C{\r}\N- He likes to say P.C. instead of press conference. - And if you do--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.32,0:21:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果你...{\r}\N- The lieutenant loves to abbreviate. - And if you do...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.66,0:21:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果你正好和他说话的话 请随时都要注意礼貌{\r}\Nhappen to speak with him, please be polite and to the point at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.26,0:21:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}确定，长官{\r}\N- Affirmative, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.60,0:21:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}确定，好{\r}\N- "Affirmative, sir." Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.73,0:21:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好{\r}\NOkay. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.80,0:21:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}11月的劳军是谁？{\r}\NWho do we have slated for live entertainment in November?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.21,0:21:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们本来希望是鲍伯.贺伯{\r}\NWell, we originally wanted Bob Hope, but it turns out he won't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.88,0:21:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但是，结果他不来 为什么？ 他不扮演警方行动，只有战争{\r}\N- Why not? - He doesn't play police actions, just wars.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.22,0:21:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}鲍伯喜欢大空间，长官{\r}\N- Bob likes a big room, sir. - [ All Laughing ]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.12,0:21:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这不好笑{\r}\NThat is not funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.19,0:21:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}扩大如何？{\r}\NHow about if it escalated?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.56,0:21:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}什么扩大如何？{\r}\N- How about if what escalated?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.63,0:21:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}越南的冲突{\r}\N- The Vietnam conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.43,0:21:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}越南的冲突？{\r}\NThe Vietnam conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.50,0:21:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们不准为了要一位大牌的明星{\r}\NWe are not going to escalate a whole war just 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.97,0:21:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}而将战争扩大{\r}\Nso we can book a big-name comedian!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.54,0:21:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们可以找汤尼.班奈或{\r}\NWe can get Tony Bennett
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.81,0:21:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}崔尼.罗佩斯{\r}\Nor Trini Lopez.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.08,0:21:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}想到了，杰瑞{\r}\NI got it. Jerry Vale.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.91,0:21:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他18号结束表演{\r}\NHe closes the Copa on the 18th.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.38,0:22:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那日期确定吗？{\r}\N- Is that date firm?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.62,0:22:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我侄女告诉我的{\r}\N- I got it from my niece.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.15,0:22:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这不是三脚猫的把戏{\r}\NThis is not the Catskills. Get somebody good. 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.32,0:22:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}找海滩男孩来，别胡来了{\r}\NGet The Beach Boys. - Don't dick around.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.12,0:22:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们试过了，但经纪人说{\r}\N- Oh, we tried, but their agent says...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.62,0:22:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他们还在沙滩上， 11月才有空{\r}\Nthey're still on the beach and they won't be off the sand 'til November! Ba-da-bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.96,0:22:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是不是有人穿了我的制服{\r}\NDidn't somebody wearing my uniform and bearing a striking
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.46,0:22:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}配上我的阶级代表我个人{\r}\Nresemblance to myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.86,0:22:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}而说这种音乐不适当吗？{\r}\Njust say that that kind of music was inappropriate?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.77,0:22:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}抱歉，长官，我还没有睡觉{\r}\NSorry, sir. I haven't been to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.21,0:22:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}前任副总统周五来此{\r}\N-The former V.P. will be here on Friday. -[ Garlick Laughing ]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.01,0:22:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我期望副总统的记者招待会{\r}\NI expect every minute of the V.P '.'S P.C. to be taped and broadcast...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.44,0:22:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}将在他到达后12小时内播出{\r}\Nwithin 12 hours of his arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.91,0:22:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有什么好笑的吗？加利{\r}\NSomething funny, Garlick?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.22,0:22:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}也许你能和大家分享一下{\r}\NWell, perhaps you'd like to share it with the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.45,0:22:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不，长官，前任副总统令人兴奋{\r}\NNo, sir. The former vice president is a delight, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.69,0:22:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对不起，长官{\r}\NExcuse me, sir. Seeing as how
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.26,0:22:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}既然V.P是VIP{\r}\Nthe V.P. is such a V.I.P.,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.73,0:22:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们是否该将V.P的事Q.T{\r}\Nshouldn't we keep the P.C. on the Q.T.,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.19,0:22:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}因泄露给V.C就会变成MIA{\r}\N'cause if it leaks to the V.C.,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.36,0:22:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那时我们就会变成K.P{\r}\Nhe could end up an M.I.A., and then we'd all be put on K.P.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.61,0:23:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想离开了{\r}\N- I would like to leave the room now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.11,0:23:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是，长官{\r}\N- Oh, yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.52,0:23:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Oh, what a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.86,0:23:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you d-d-d-do--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.36,0:23:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果你是的话{\r}\N- And if you do-- - [ All ] And if you do--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.86,0:23:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这里是艾迪和雷康尼夫选辑{\r}\NEddie Kirk here,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.77,0:23:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}马上就播放了{\r}\Nand Ray Conniff jubilee coming up in just a few moments.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.50,0:23:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我说选辑，其实是最新的唱片{\r}\NI call it a jubilee. Actually, it's a Ray Conniff featurette.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.91,0:23:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}3 ，也许4个顶尖的雷康尼夫{\r}\NThree, maybe four, back-to-back 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.81,0:23:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}经典之作{\r}\NRay Conniff classics.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.53,0:23:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们到了，吉米，握哈！{\r}\N[ Garlick ] We're here, sir. Jimmy Wah's.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.74,0:24:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这是我们喜欢来的地方{\r}\NThis is the place where we like to hang out, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.34,0:24:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}很热闹，有点鸦片馆的样子{\r}\NReal homey, in an opium kind of way.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.44,0:24:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}厄尔.吉米，他是老板{\r}\N- Earl! Earl! Earl! - That's Jimmy Wah. He owns the place. Hi! Hi! Hi! Hi! Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.95,0:24:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}现在该你对我说哈，然后微笑{\r}\N- Now you say hi to me, then you smile. - [ Together ] Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.02,0:24:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}二位厄尔，要来杯酒吗？{\r}\NHey, you two Earl. What about a couple of beer?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.42,0:24:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们很喜欢来二杯酒，吉米{\r}\NWe'd love a couple of beers, Jimmy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.03,0:24:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们为何叫做厄尔？{\r}\N- Are either of our names "Earl"?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.33,0:24:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}大家都是厄尔{\r}\N- He calls everybody Earl.
