Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.92,0:55:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你能告诉我们从你来这里之后{\r}\NCan you tell us what you've found out about
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.52,0:55:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你对敌人有何发现{\r}\N the enemy since you've been here?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.05,0:55:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们发现我们找不到他们{\r}\N"We found out that we can't find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.02,0:55:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他们在外面{\r}\NThey're out there, and we're having a major difficulty...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.59,0:55:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们在找寻敌人方面非常的困难{\r}\Nin finding the enemy."
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.53,0:55:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你是利用什么去找他们？{\r}\NWell, what do you use to look for them?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.13,0:55:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们询问人民，你是敌人吗？{\r}\N"Well, we ask people, 'Are you the enemy?'
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.20,0:55:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}只要说是的人，我们就开枪打他{\r}\NAnd whoever says yes, we shoot them."
