Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.21,0:55:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}很不容易找到叫查理的越南人{\r}\N"It's very difficult to find a Vietnamese man named Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.51,0:55:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他们全叫诺南，道，诸如此类的{\r}\NThey're all named Nyugen or Doh or things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.48,0:56:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对我来说很困难{\r}\NIt's very difficult for me."
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.35,0:56:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,# Coming home It feels nice ##
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.59,0:56:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是否属实，你真的...{\r}\NIs it true that you've actually, um--
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.96,0:56:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}离他们在实验的神经气体太近了{\r}\NYou're actually too close to some of the nerve agents they were testing?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.53,0:56:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}神经...毒气？{\r}\N"Nerve-- uh, gas?"
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.83,0:56:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是，你是否用过？{\r}\NYes, have you used any?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.83,0:56:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}一次，对我自己，但没有...{\r}\N"Well, once, yes, on myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.90,0:56:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对我没有奏效{\r}\NAnd it had no-- Whoa! Whoa! No effect on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.74,0:56:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我说没有实际的...{\r}\NI've had no actual-- Whoa! She-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.74,0:56:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}大狗帖在我脸上{\r}\NWhoa! Whoa! Big dogs! Big dogs landing on my face!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.81,0:56:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不知那是什么意思？{\r}\NI don't know what that means."
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.68,0:56:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}嘿，时间到了，我要走了{\r}\NHey, that's it for me. I'm out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.89,0:56:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}艾德伦.康纳时间到了{\r}\NThat's the end of the Adrian Cron Hour, but I'm gonna turn you over to Mr. Warmth,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.55,0:56:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我现在交给丹.拉文登{\r}\NDan "The Tan" Levitan!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.23,0:56:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}非常感谢，艾德伦{\r}\N[ Laughs ] Thank you so much, Adrian.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.13,0:56:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}艾德伦.康纳是本台K{\r}\NAdrian Cronauer, G.I.s,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.50,0:56:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}深受官兵喜爱的疯狂主持人{\r}\Na wacky and welcome addition...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.03,0:56:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}尼克森的记者招待会{\r}\N- to AFRS, Radio Saigon. - Nixon's press conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.97,0:56:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你听听看，他几乎快要真诚了{\r}\NWait 'til you hear it. He's this far from sincerity.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.94,0:56:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我去填点东西{\r}\NNo, man, listen. Let me just feed my face. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.51,0:57:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你要去那里？{\r}\NWhere do you imagine you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.41,0:57:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}去吃点东西{\r}\N- Just going to get a little something to eat. - You don't have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.01,0:57:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你没有时间，你在这里吃速食面{\r}\NYou'll stay here and drink instant beverage or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.65,0:57:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们答应听众在下午4点时{\r}\NWe promised our listening
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.22,0:57:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}倾听尼克森的谈话{\r}\Naudience Nixon highlights by 4:00 p.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.09,0:57:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我已广播了4小时，有点饿了{\r}\NI've been on the air for four hours. I'm a little hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.42,0:57:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那是笑语，对不？我明白了{\r}\N- That's a joke, right? I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.43,0:57:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不，我真的饿了{\r}\N- No, I'm actually hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.50,0:57:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我真的下命令给你{\r}\NWell, I'm actually giving you an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.67,0:57:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是命令，这样的话，策划吧{\r}\NOh, it's an order. In that case, gentlemen, let's edit. Oh, it's an order. In that case, gentlemen, let's edit.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.18,0:57:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谢谢{\r}\NThank you. Mm-mmm, Campbell's
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.51,0:57:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aha! Ha! Earl!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.38,0:57:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}又是你，不再打架了，好吗？{\r}\NHa, you again. No more fighting, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.82,0:57:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你换衣服了，不错的发亮绿西装{\r}\NOh, you got-- James! Nice, shiny green suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.25,0:57:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你看来像人妖{\r}\N- You look like an Oriental leprechaun. - You like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.22,0:57:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你喜欢吗？我由香港弄来的{\r}\NI got it in Hong Kong,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.16,0:57:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}发亮绿西装之家{\r}\Nhome of the shiny green suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.33,0:57:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}所以南越没中立的空间{\r}\N[ Nixon On Radio ] And therefore, there is no place for neutrality...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.47,0:57:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}也没有中立的妥协{\r}\Nor a neutralist sentiment in South Vietnam.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.74,0:57:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我在今日离开越南的同时{\r}\NAs I leave Vietnam today, 
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.21,0:58:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在我脑海中毫无疑问的{\r}\Nthere is no doubt, certainly, in my mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.81,0:58:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}越共将会被击败{\r}\N- That's Nixon. - but that the Viet Cong will be defeated...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.24,0:58:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这场战争也会打赢{\r}\Nand that this war will be won.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.88,0:58:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这个题目尚包括了{\r}\NAsia does involve, I think,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.22,0:58:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}正如你所建议的，赋予与夺取{\r}\Nvery appropriately as you have suggested, give and take.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.82,0:58:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我其实没有作此建议，对不起{\r}\N[ Cronauer ] I really didn't make that suggestion, sir. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.95,0:58:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}美国政府没有权力赋予{\r}\N[ Nixon ] The United States has no right to give.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.36,0:58:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}康纳的声音为何出现在录音带中{\r}\N- Why would Cronauer's voice be on this tape? - I don't know, Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.16,0:58:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不知道，中尉{\r}\N[ Nixon ]...its territory to the Communists.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.00,0:58:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谢谢你这番政治性发言{\r}\N[ Cronauer ] Mr. Nixon, thank you for that concise political commentary,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.47,0:58:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但我想谈一些较私人性的话题{\r}\Nbut I'd like to delve into
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.93,0:58:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}为了那些在战场上的弟兄{\r}\Nsomething slightly more personal for the men in the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.64,0:58:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你会如何形容你的生殖器？{\r}\NHow would you describe your testicles?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.77,0:58:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}软软的，浅薄，没有目的{\r}\N[ Nixon ] That they're soft, that they're shallow, that they have no purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.78,0:58:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我的天呀  你是在说什么？{\r}\N- Oh, my God. - [ Cronauer ] What are you saying, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.08,0:58:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}它缺少体能上的冲劲{\r}\N[ Nixon ] That they lack the physical strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.35,0:58:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你会如何形容你的性生活？{\r}\N- How would you describe your sex life with your wife Pat?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.25,0:58:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有时候不太刺激{\r}\N- Uh, it is unexciting sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.52,0:58:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你是否考虑过变性手术...{\r}\NWell, have you considered a sex change? There is an operation that can transform you...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.39,0:58:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}求求你别这样对待我，求求你{\r}\N- Please don't do this to me. - into a female Great Dane... - Please don't do this to me! - or a very well-hung Chihuahua.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.59,0:58:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}尼克森先生，既然你来到越南{\r}\NMr. Nixon, while you've been in Vietnam,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.39,0:58:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谣传你抽大麻{\r}\Nit's rumored that you smoked marijuana.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.70,0:59:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你计划带些大麻回美国的家中吗{\r}\NAre you planning, sir, to take some of the marijuana home, back to the United States?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.70,0:59:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你要如何办到？{\r}\N- How would you do that? - [ Nixon ] By plane,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.77,0:59:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}用飞机，直升机{\r}\Nby helicopter and also by automobile.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.54,0:59:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}同时还用汽车{\r}\NI was wondering if you could do your Mr. Ed, because I know people love that.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.11,0:59:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}关掉，我说关掉{\r}\NCut that thing off. I said cut it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.94,0:59:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}康纳呢？{\r}\N- Sir. - Where is Cronauer?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.71,0:59:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}还在吃饭，长官{\r}\N- Still eating, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.32,0:59:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我要ASAP见他{\r}\N- I want to see him A.S.A.P.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.75,0:59:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}什么？长官{\r}\N- What, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.32,0:59:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}尽快！{\r}\N- As soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.66,0:59:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}VG，长官{\r}\N- V.G., sir. - We interrupt this broadcast...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.29,0:59:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们中断这段广播{\r}\Nto bring you an emergency selection
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.63,0:59:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}因有紧急的选歌{\r}\Nof the Benny Goodman Orchestra.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.86,0:59:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们需考虑不再让他广播{\r}\N[ Hauk ] We simply need to consider taking him off the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.43,0:59:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}中尉，我们每周都接到{\r}\N[ Taylor ] Lieutenant, we get hundreds, maybe thousands of calls and letters each week.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.33,0:59:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}上千封信和电话，歌迷信件 他是军中电台有史以来 第一位有歌迷邮件的人{\r}\NFan mail. He's the first man in the history of Armed Forces Radio to get fan mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.37,0:59:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这个国家的每位大兵{\r}\NEvery G.I. in this country
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.08,0:59:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}每天都听他一天二次的节目{\r}\Nis glued to his radio twice a day...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.68,0:59:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在0600和1600时{\r}\Nat 0600 hours and 1600 hours
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.05,0:59:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}去收听那个疯子{\r}\Nto hear that lunatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.28,0:59:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}长官，那人有不敬的趋向{\r}\NSir, the man has got an irreverent tendency.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.72,0:59:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他对前任副总统尼克森{\r}\NHe did a very off-color
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.79,0:59:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}作了十分讽刺的言论{\r}\Nparody of former V.P. Nixon.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.52,0:59:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我以为是热闹{\r}\N- I thought it was hilarious.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.36,0:59:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}诚心尊重，长官{\r}\N- Respectfully, sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.56,1:00:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}前任副总统是位好人和正直的人{\r}\Nthe former V.P. is a good man and a decent man.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.06,1:00:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}狗屁！我本人认识他{\r}\NBullshit! I know Nixon personally.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.27,1:00:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他留下的狗屁事足可制造毒气了{\r}\NHe lugs a trainload of shit behind him that would fertilize the Sinai.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.87,1:00:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我连苹果也不会向那王八蛋买{\r}\NI wouldn't buy an apple from the son of a bitch, 
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.64,1:00:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我还视他是位好朋友{\r}\Nand I consider him a close, personal friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.27,1:00:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们谈谈正事吧，是怎么回事？{\r}\NLet's get down to business here, General. What the hell's goin' on here?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.08,1:00:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这件事情非同小可{\r}\NWe've got a mounting crisis in this country.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.68,1:00:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有位深受弟兄们欢迎的D. J{\r}\N We've got a deejay that the men dearly love.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.08,1:00:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如你们有私人恩怨的话去解决掉{\r}\NIf you two have personal problems, solve them, will you?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.65,1:00:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谢谢你，中尉{\r}\NThank you, Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.36,1:00:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谢谢你，中尉{\r}\NThank you, Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.63,1:00:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}说出来吧，迪克{\r}\NSpeak your piece, Dick.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.80,1:00:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不是不尊重你，长官{\r}\NDue respect, sir. 
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.60,1:00:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我在军中已有15年指挥经验{\r}\NI have over 15 years command experience in this army.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.80,1:00:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你真的要我不说话也不做事{\r}\NDo you really expect me to run this radio station with nothin'
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.07,1:00:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}来管理这个电台吗？{\r}\Nto say and no way to do it?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.28,1:00:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}目前是如此{\r}\NRight now, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.68,1:00:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是，长官{\r}\NY es, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.35,1:01:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这件事还没结束{\r}\NThis is not over yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.89,1:01:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If somebody wants you
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.89,1:01:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你怎么还在这里？{\r}\N- Why are you still here?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.09,1:01:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你说什么{\r}\N- Sparky.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.13,1:01:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我正放轻松的喝杯老酒...{\r}\N Sittin' back, havin' a cup of formaldehyde here.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.66,1:01:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你说我们要碰面谈陈的事{\r}\NYou say after you go out with Trinh, you meet me to talk and discuss about her.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.60,1:01:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没什么好谈的，她不喜欢我{\r}\N- There's nothing to discuss. She doesn't like me.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.87,1:01:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她喜欢{\r}\N- Yes, she do.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.14,1:01:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她不喜欢我{\r}\N- No, she don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.97,1:01:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她喜欢，她今天要见你{\r}\N- She do liking you. She want to meet you today.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.00,1:01:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}离此不远{\r}\N- She's not far from here.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.41,1:01:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我4点还要回去广播{\r}\N- I can't. I gotta be back on the air again at 4:00.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.71,1:01:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}今天去见她，否则错过大机会{\r}\NYou have to meet her today. Otherwise you miss your big chance.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.88,1:01:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我可不想错过大机会{\r}\N- Don't want to miss my big chance.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.31,1:01:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对，来，走{\r}\N- Yes. Come. We go.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.75,1:01:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你好像跟印弟安人学的英文{\r}\N- You sound like you learned English from Tonto. "Come. We go." - Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.45,1:01:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我仍不相信她真的要见我{\r}\NI still can't believe she really wants to see me.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.85,1:01:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对{\r}\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.99,1:01:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想那海滩电影感动了她{\r}\N- I guess that beach movie really impressed her, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.83,1:01:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我要送她东西{\r}\NI gotta get her something.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.73,1:01:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}香蕉如何？{\r}\NUh, what about bananas?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.26,1:01:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不，这会导致误解{\r}\N- No. - No, that doesn't say the right thing. You're right. How 'bout--
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.44,1:01:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}“1430时发生爆炸K”{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.17,1:02:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}“爆炸发生在吉米的酒吧K”{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.88,1:02:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}“此酒吧为美军常去的休闲场所”{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.88,1:02:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}“据报导一枚塑胶炸弹毁了酒吧”{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.85,1:02:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}“美军人员三人受伤两人身亡”{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.75,1:02:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我的酒吧{\r}\NOh, my bar!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.62,1:02:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}为什么要这么做？{\r}\NWhy they do that?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.74,1:03:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你不能把他丢在这{\r}\N- You can't just leave 'em in this shit here. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.27,1:03:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他已死了{\r}\N- This boy's gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.12,1:03:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}退后{\r}\NGet back.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.59,1:03:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...fire is worse, and the fire is lapping the outside of the building.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.08,1:03:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他去那里？{\r}\NHey, where's he going?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.48,1:03:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你在干什么？你也知不能念K{\r}\NWhat do you think you're doing? You know you're forbidden to read anything not checked by--
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.75,1:03:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有什么好检查的，我在场{\r}\N- What's there to check? I was there. It happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.32,1:03:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你知道规定{\r}\N- Airman, you know the rules.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.42,1:04:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}正当的新闻要由适当管道播出{\r}\NIf this is a legitimate news story, it must go through proper channels.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.02,1:04:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}听着，笨蛋，你以为这那来的？{\r}\NListen, Tweedle-dee, it's an actual event. Where do you think this came from, shaving?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.09,1:04:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}刮脸吗？是真相{\r}\NIt's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.26,1:04:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我只要报导真相来改变一下{\r}\NI just want to report the truth. It'd be a nice change of pace.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.50,1:04:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}怎么回事？{\r}\N- What's goin' on here?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.26,1:04:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}长官，你听我说好吗？{\r}\N- Sir, will you listen to me?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.84,1:04:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这不是官方新闻{\r}\NThis is not official news, Airman.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.17,1:04:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}就我所知这没有发生 发生了{\r}\N As far as I'm concerned, it didn't happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.84,1:04:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你闭嘴{\r}\N- It did happen-- - You shut your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.01,1:04:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你怕什么？迪克生{\r}\NWhat are you afraid of, Dickerson?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.01,1:04:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}怕人们发现有战争在进行？{\r}\NPeople might find out there's a war goin' on?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.41,1:04:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这新闻不是官方的{\r}\NThis news is not official, Airman.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.48,1:04:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你要人们相信此地很安全，对不{\r}\NYou want everyone going under the assumption it's perfectly safe here, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.61,1:04:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但不是，战斗不只在山上{\r}\NWell, it's not. The fighting's not just in the hills.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.65,1:04:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}城里也是K{\r}\NIt's downtown. It's a couple of fuckin' blocks--
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.72,1:04:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我说那不关你的事{\r}\NI said it is none of your goddamn business!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.79,1:04:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我明白你的意思了{\r}\NI see your point.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.89,1:04:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}抱歉{\r}\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.99,1:04:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想一进来被冷气吹的头昏了{\r}\NI guess I get inside, hit these air conditioners, I get a little dizzy.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.87,1:04:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谢谢你们纠正了我{\r}\NThanks for settin' me straight.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.20,1:04:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我没事了{\r}\NI'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.31,1:04:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That about wraps it up for me, Marty Lee, filling in for my buddy...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.51,1:04:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,vacationing Eddie Kirk, who, despite all your requests, will return tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.15,1:05:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, it's once again time for the King Kong of Saigon,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.58,1:05:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Adrian Cronauer.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.46,1:05:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}早安，越南{\r}\NGood morning, Vietnam!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.30,1:05:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我知道不是早上，这是我的招牌{\r}\NHey, I know it's not the morning, but that's my trademark...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.87,1:05:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}午安听起来太消沉了{\r}\Nand "good evening" sounds too depressing.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.67,1:05:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}现在报新闻{\r}\NHey, we're goin' right now to the news. [ lmitating Teletype ]
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.87,1:05:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}来自英国，今天...{\r}\N[ Sighs ] From England, today...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.08,1:05:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}马格莉特公主丢了一只鞋{\r}\NPrincess Margaret threw a shoe!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.15,1:05:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别激动，马姬{\r}\NEasy, Madge. Also, uh, Elizab--
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.28,1:05:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}同时，伊莉莎白皇后...{\r}\NQueen Elizabeth, Liz, Elizabeth Taylor!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.65,1:05:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}伊莉莎白.泰勒{\r}\NElizabeth Taylor.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.48,1:05:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}结婚6个月后还仍维持着{\r}\NShe's still married after six months.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.69,1:05:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不错，伊莉{\r}\N- Way to go, Liz. Hey! - [ Squealing ]
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.02,1:05:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对！今日的西贡{\r}\NAll right! In Saigon today, according to official sources, All right! In Saigon today, according to official sources,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.49,1:05:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}根据官方的消息是一切平安{\r}\Nnothing actually happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.56,1:05:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}一件官方上没有发生的事是{\r}\NOne thing that didn't officially happen
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.86,1:05:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}一个炸弹并没有正式的爆炸{\r}\Nwas a bomb didn't officially explode...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.50,1:05:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在1430时没有正式的摧毁了{\r}\Nat 1430 hours, unofficially destroying
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.70,1:05:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}吉米咖啡厅{\r}\N Jimmy Wah's Cafe.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.70,1:05:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}把他赶出去{\r}\N- Get him out of there.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.87,1:05:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}非正式报导了人受伤{\r}\N- Three men were unofficially wounded, and two men...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.51,1:05:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有二人的身份至目前仍不清楚{\r}\Nwhose identities are still not known at this time are unofficially dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.21,1:06:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}非正式的被杀了  把门撞开 警方和消防队的报告{\r}\N- Break the goddamn door down. - Although the police, ambulance and fire department responded,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.58,1:06:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但已据信在此刻是非官方的{\r}\Nit's believed to be unofficial at this present moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.68,1:06:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}把开关关掉，马上关掉{\r}\NTurn the power off in that studio. Turn it off! Now!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.79,1:06:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我只是认为你们该...{\r}\N[ Cronauer ] I just wanted to think that you should--
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.94,1:07:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那人该送军法{\r}\NThe man should be court-martialed, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.87,1:07:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你们认为这是本周我该处理的{\r}\NYou think this is the most serious set of affairs I have to address this week?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.04,1:07:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}最严重事件K不是{\r}\N- Well, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.67,1:07:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不相信你要放过此事，将军{\r}\N- I can't believe you're gonna pass on this, General.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.28,1:07:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那人是颠复份子{\r}\N- The man is a goddamned subversive.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.58,1:07:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他犯了个错误{\r}\N- He made a mistake, Dick.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.75,1:07:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}错误？当他报导我们军队动向时{\r}\NMistake, sir? I don't want to be around when he broadcasts U.S. troop movements...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.81,1:07:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我可不想在场{\r}\Nto the other side.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.88,1:07:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我是严格遵守由军方情报处规定{\r}\NI run the station according to strict
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.85,1:07:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}来管理电台的{\r}\Nguidelines set by military intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.19,1:07:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}军方情报处？{\r}\NMilitary intelligence?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.39,1:07:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这倒是种矛盾的语气{\r}\NThere's a contradiction in terms.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.12,1:07:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}长官，那人是个活动炸弹{\r}\NSir, the man is a walking keg of dynamite.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.32,1:07:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在他广播中的8周里{\r}\NIn the eight weeks he's been on the air, General,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.13,1:07:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他以违背命令作为风格{\r}\N he's disobeyed orders as to style and content.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.50,1:07:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他报非官方的新闻{\r}\NHe's read unofficial news.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.96,1:07:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}6个月后他会变成怎样？{\r}\NWhat's he gonna be like in six months?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.17,1:07:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他变成十倍受欢迎时该怎么办？{\r}\NWhat's he gonna be like when he's ten times as popular, General?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.97,1:07:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那时要他不广播会很容易吗？{\r}\NHow easy is it gonna be to get him off the air then?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.34,1:07:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谁来接康纳的节目呢？{\r}\NWho'll do the Cronauer show?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.14,1:07:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}哈克能{\r}\NWell, Hauk can do it, sir,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.98,1:07:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}直到我找到接替人选{\r}\Ntill I find a replacement.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.35,1:07:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好，现在起停他职{\r}\NOkay, for now, suspend him.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.21,1:07:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}长官，你做了正确的选择{\r}\NSir, you've made the correct choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.22,1:07:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, right here on our show, Diana Ross and the "Suprawns."
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.32,1:07:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Set me free why don't you, babe
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.62,1:07:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Set me free why don't you, babe
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.19,1:08:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't really need me You just keep me steamin' on
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.53,1:08:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much. Let me introduce the members of the band. Larry, Pisces.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.10,1:08:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- [ Speaking Vietnamese ]
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.10,1:08:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他说什么？ 他说你已喝多了{\r}\N- What'd he say? - He say you drink too much already.
