Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.50,1:08:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想看你们的生活不会使我高兴{\r}\NI don't think seeing your little production of Our Town is gonna cheer me up.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.74,1:08:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你能看到陈{\r}\N- You see Trinh there.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.50,1:08:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我开车{\r}\N- I'll drive.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.04,1:08:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}红皮，黄皮...{\r}\NRed leather, yellow leather. Red-- Led-- Red, red leather, yellow leather.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.84,1:08:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}长官，报新闻是一回事{\r}\N- Red leather, yellow leather-- - Sir, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.85,1:08:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但你写的那东西不好笑，很悲哀{\r}\NReading the news is one thing, but this stuff you wrote, i-it's not funny, sir. It's sad.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.68,1:08:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}长官，我求你，别当滑稽客{\r}\NSir? I'm begging you. Don't try to do comedy. 
