Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.42,1:08:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我会做的很好{\r}\NI'll do fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.49,1:08:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}喜剧是创造出来的{\r}\NComedy is what you make it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.69,1:09:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我有好多页的上好题材，对不？{\r}\NI've got pages and pages of great material. Right, Abersold?
