Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.36,1:09:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如不好笑的话{\r}\NIf it isn't funny, 
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.36,1:09:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}为何你们在打字时我听见笑声{\r}\Nthen why did l hear you laughing when you typed it?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.53,1:09:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我在想别的事{\r}\NI was thinking of something else.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.07,1:09:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谢谢你的支持，我有节目要做了{\r}\NThank you for your support. Now I've got a show to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.54,1:09:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}长官，你不风趣，打听一下{\r}\NSir, you're not funny. Ask around.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.94,1:09:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}问我，我们都很尊敬你，长官{\r}\NAsk me. Sir, with all due respect,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.98,1:09:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你也许能下蛋，大蛋{\r}\Nuh, I think you're gonna-- you might lay an egg-- I mean a big egg.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.44,1:09:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我了解风趣，我不认为你是{\r}\NI mean, I know funny, and I don't think you're it. But hey, such is life.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.51,1:09:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}就像我，我对工具就不内行K{\r}\NMe, I'm not much with power tools.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.32,1:09:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那是派图.克拉的精彩歌曲{\r}\NHey, that was the great, exciting sound of Petula Clark.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.89,1:09:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}海滩少年，是那些人才对{\r}\N- Beach Boys. Those were guys. - Of The Beach Boys.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.96,1:09:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}海滩少年！我的时间到了{\r}\NHey, that wraps it up for me, Marty Lee Dreiwitz.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.69,1:09:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}艾德伦.康纳外出执行短暂任务{\r}\NAdrian Cronauer is on temporary assignment,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.20,1:09:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但我有个大惊喜给你们{\r}\Nbut boy, do I have a surprise for you.
