Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.68,1:09:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}哈，越南{\r}\NHello, Vietnam. And greetings.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.55,1:09:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}欢迎！不久就报新闻{\r}\NSoon, the news. Then:
