Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.22,1:10:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那一位？{\r}\N[ American Accent ] Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.42,1:10:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是我，你的老友法国人{\r}\NIt's me, your old pal Frenchy. 
