Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.66,1:10:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那我想你就是美食主义者了{\r}\NWell, then, I guess that would make you an "Eatie Gourmet."
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.37,1:10:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}史帝中尉...{\r}\N- [ Honking Horn ] - Oh, ho, ho, ho, Lieutenant Steve.
