Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.25,1:10:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}史帝中尉，我们来点音乐吧{\r}\NUh, Lieutenant Steve, let's play some music.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.02,1:10:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好，法国人，你想听什么？{\r}\NOkay, Frenchy. What would you like to hear?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.72,1:10:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我喜欢波卡舞曲正如喜欢身旁人{\r}\NWell, uh, I love a good polka as much as the next man.
