Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.81,1:11:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想有人该道歉了吧{\r}\NI think some apologies are in order.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.92,1:11:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你不会还想继续广播下去吧{\r}\NYou're not gonna continue this broadcast, are you, sir?
