Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.83,1:12:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他们打坐，祈求和平，智慧知识{\r}\Nfor peace, wisdom and knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.60,1:12:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他们在等待启发{\r}\NThey're waiting for enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.69,1:12:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这人的儿子被美军地雷炸死{\r}\NThis man lose one son from blasting American mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.36,1:12:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他父亲和哥哥在很久以前{\r}\NHis father and brother
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.70,1:12:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}被法国人杀死{\r}\Nwas killed by French long ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.50,1:12:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这对他很不公平{\r}\NI think it's not fair to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.73,1:13:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}看{\r}\NLook. [ Laughing ]
