Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.40,1:14:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你不了解{\r}\NYou not understand. You not.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.21,1:14:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们在一起没有前途{\r}\NWe... no future together, Cronow.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.48,1:14:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我的国家也许没有前途{\r}\NMy country, maybe no future.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.15,1:14:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我喜欢你，我只想当你的朋友{\r}\NHey, I like you. I just want to be your friend, okay?
