Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.77,1:15:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这是你们所听到最好的波卡舞曲{\r}\NThat's about as good a polka as you'll ever hear.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.01,1:16:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你要康纳再广播？{\r}\NYou want Cronauer back on the air.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.05,1:16:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你要康纳再广播...{\r}\NYou want Cronauer back on the air.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.68,1:16:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们有二大袋的邮件{\r}\NWe've gotten duffel bags filled with information, 
