Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.72,1:16:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}大家全恨哈克{\r}\NThe men all hate Hauk.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.39,1:16:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他们要康纳回来{\r}\NThey want Cronauer back.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.92,1:16:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他是位振奋精神的人{\r}\NHe's an exhilarating personality,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.36,1:16:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}波卡舞曲是替代不了的{\r}\Nand polkas are just no substitute.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.86,1:16:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想我要看个范例{\r}\NI think I see a pattern forming here.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.03,1:16:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这些信件太露骨了{\r}\NSir, these letters are unequivocal. Uh, e.g.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.16,1:16:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}哈克，去吃一袋粪，你真烂{\r}\N"Hey, Hauk, eat a bag of shit. You suck."
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.80,1:16:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这已表明重点了，没什么好说{\r}\NThat's pretty much to the point, sir. Not much gray area in this one.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.87,1:16:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们只接到一通肯定的电话{\r}\NWe got one positive call from some guy in Wichita...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.30,1:16:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他认为哈克的笑语是空中阁楼{\r}\Nwho thought Hauk's comedy was visionary and interesting.
