Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.91,1:16:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这是直接引过的，长官{\r}\NThat's a direct quote, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.65,1:16:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我今早接了90通电话{\r}\NI've taken 90 calls this morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.21,1:16:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他们不喜欢哈克{\r}\NThey just don't like Hauk.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.45,1:16:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}越南部队{\r}\NFrom a marine in Da Nang
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.95,1:16:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}哈克中尉把死人的睾丸也吓干了{\r}\N: "Captain Hauk sucks the sweat off a dead man's balls."
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.95,1:16:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不知那是什么意思，但是{\r}\NI have no idea what that means, sir,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.06,1:16:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我看来那非常的否定{\r}\Nbut it seems very negative to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.09,1:16:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想部队是想告诉我们一件事{\r}\NI think the troops are tryin' to tell us somethin', fellas.
