Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.20,1:17:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我认为部份被康纳的摇滚乐 所分裂的人不代表全体{\r}\Nweren't represented by Cronauer's broadcasts of rock and roll.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.07,1:17:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但我可以偶而放盖瑞路易斯的歌{\r}\NBut I can easily play an occasional Gary Lewis record.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.28,1:17:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你放不放波卡舞曲没多大差别{\r}\NIt doesn't make a damn whether you play polkas or don't play polkas.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.94,1:17:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}军中的政治，不是针对你个人{\r}\NMilitary politics. Nothing personal.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.61,1:17:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}大家比较喜欢他，不喜欢你{\r}\NThe men just like him better than they do you.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.38,1:17:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他故意的播报非官方的新闻{\r}\NHe maliciously and with purposeful intent read unofficial news.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.32,1:17:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不，不，他犯了个错误{\r}\NNo, no, no, no. He made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.99,1:17:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们全会犯错{\r}\NWe all make mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.12,1:17:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}现在的情况是很敏感的平衡状况{\r}\N Now this thing is a delicate balance over here,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.96,1:17:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不要全依赖一位播音员{\r}\Nand I don't want it dependent on a disc jockey.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.80,1:17:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}弟兄要他回来，我就要他回来{\r}\NThe men want him back, I want him back.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.10,1:17:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}长官{\r}\NSir, 
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.07,1:17:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你只听到不喜欢我那种幽默的人{\r}\Nyou heard from the men who don't like my humor,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.44,1:17:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那些沉默大众喜欢我的人呢？{\r}\N but what about the silent masses who do?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.80,1:17:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}至于波卡舞曲{\r}\NAnd as far as polkas, 
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.44,1:17:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}音乐品味较高{\r}\Nthey are a much-maligned musical taste.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.78,1:17:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}中尉，你是东南西北分不清{\r}\NLieutenant, you don't know whether you're shot, fucked, powder-burned or snake-bit.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.78,1:17:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我才不在乎波卡舞曲{\r}\NI don't care about polkas.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.78,1:17:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他们在大声叫喊{\r}\NThey're rioting in Hue. 
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.18,1:17:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们每个月有上千部队来此{\r}\NWe're bringin' in thousands of troops every month.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.95,1:17:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}西贡的恐怖活动增加了{\r}\NTerrorism's on the uprise in Saigon.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.32,1:17:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}此国家问题和你放不放波卡舞曲{\r}\NThe problems of this country have not one goddamned thing to do with...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.62,1:17:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}一点也没有关系{\r}\Nwhether you play polkas or don't play polkas.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.83,1:18:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}弟兄要他回来，我要他回来{\r}\NThe men want him back. I want him back.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.06,1:18:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}让他复职{\r}\NReinstate the man.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.07,1:18:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}长官{\r}\NSir, in my heart,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.87,1:18:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在我内心里，我知我很风趣{\r}\NI know I'm funny.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.80,1:18:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谢谢你，中尉{\r}\NThank you, Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.08,1:18:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你在此，长官{\r}\N- There you are, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.18,1:18:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}拜托别叫我长官{\r}\N- Please don't call me "sir."
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.95,1:18:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我刚由总部回来，你又要广播了{\r}\N- It just came down the pike. You're back on the air, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.55,1:18:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不做了{\r}\N- I'm not goin' on.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.56,1:18:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不做了是什么意思？{\r}\NWhat do you mean you're not goin' on?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.36,1:18:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}听不明白？{\r}\NIf you don't understand what I said,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.43,1:18:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}也许该参加我的英文班{\r}\Nmaybe you should take my English class.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.76,1:18:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不做了{\r}\NI'm not goin' on.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.83,1:18:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你很帅，艾伯，别以为我没注意{\r}\NVery attractive man, Abersold. Don't think I haven't noticed.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.00,1:18:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你会很无聊，你要如何打发时间{\r}\N- You'll be bored, you know. What are you gonna do with your time?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.97,1:18:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不知道{\r}\N- I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.94,1:18:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}也许去城中找位叫菲尔的越南人{\r}\NI may go downtown, look for a Vietnamese man named Phil.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.61,1:18:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}或是留在这里听白藩的老唱片{\r}\NOr I may just stay here and listen to old Pat Boone records.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.71,1:18:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}试着找寻它背后的意义{\r}\NTry and find some hidden meaning
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.85,1:18:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}基本来说，我认为那人{\r}\N'cause basically I believe that
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.52,1:18:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是位被误解的天才{\r}\Nman is a misunderstood genius.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.72,1:18:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}天才？你是在对我说什么？{\r}\NGenius. What are you saying to me?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.89,1:19:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我说我不干了，艾德{\r}\NI'm sayin' I'm through, Ed.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.22,1:19:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我已厌倦别人对我说什么不能讲{\r}\N I'm tired of people tellin' me what I can't say.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.73,1:19:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这段新闻不是官方的{\r}\NThis news isn't official.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.79,1:19:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那评论太讽刺{\r}\NThat comment is too sarcastic.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.03,1:19:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我连查理.尼克森也不能开玩笑{\r}\NI can't even make fun of Richard Nixon, 
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.73,1:19:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那个人正大声叫喊着要被取笑{\r}\Nand there's a man who's screaming out to be made fun of.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.37,1:19:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}所以，何苦！{\r}\NSo fuck it. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.07,1:19:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他不要紧吗？  不，他不好{\r}\N- Is he all right? - No, Phil, he's not all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.67,1:19:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如事情顺利的话{\r}\NA man does not refer to Pat Boone
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.41,1:19:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他不会将白藩视为美丽的天才{\r}\Nas a beautiful genius if things are all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.22,1:19:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}长官{\r}\N- Sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.42,1:19:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}加利{\r}\N- Garlick?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.48,1:19:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我要你校对一下这些优先新闻稿{\r}\NI'd like you to collate these one-minute spots prior to broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.29,1:19:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你对这个有问题吗？年轻人{\r}\NYou have a problem with that, young man?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.03,1:19:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}绝对没有{\r}\N-Absolutely not. 
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.09,1:19:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我靠校对过活{\r}\NI live to collate, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.36,1:19:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好{\r}\N-Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.93,1:19:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我也是{\r}\NSo do l.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.64,1:19:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}找份工作{\r}\N- "Get A Job."
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.60,1:19:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}找份工作？再一次{\r}\N- Get a job. Again.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.04,1:19:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}找到工作K对，你出师了{\r}\NY eah, a job. Right. - You got it. You're cookin' now.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.98,1:19:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}长官？  艾伍{\r}\N- Sir? - Edward.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.38,1:19:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想要个解释{\r}\N- I'd like an explanation.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.75,1:20:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有没有什么特别的事吗？{\r}\N- On anything in particular?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.08,1:20:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}很多人要你{\r}\N- A lot of people went to the mat for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.62,1:20:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}成千的人写信来，打电话{\r}\NThousands of guys wrote in, called in,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.52,1:20:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}想让你复职{\r}\Ntryin' to get you reinstated.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.92,1:20:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我认为你亏欠他们全体{\r}\NAnd I literally think that you owe it to all of them to get your ass back on the air.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.16,1:20:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}该再回去广播{\r}\NAnd I literally think that you owe it to all of them to get your ass back on the air.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.93,1:20:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}天知道，军方不要我，艾德{\r}\NIf you haven't noticed, the Army doesn't really want me, Ed.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.57,1:20:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}从我下机那天起就在找我麻烦{\r}\NThey've been harassing me since the day I got off the plane.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.40,1:20:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}又怎样？{\r}\NSo what?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.10,1:20:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}重要的是战场上那些人，记得吗{\r}\N It's the guys in the field that matter, remember?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.47,1:20:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}死的是那些人{\r}\NThose are the guys that are dyin'.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.21,1:20:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我试着说真相，他们却赶我走{\r}\NEdward, I tried to tell the truth, and they kicked me off the air.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.34,1:20:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我再犯错，迪克会送我去打仗{\r}\NI screw up once more, Dickerson sends me into the field with a rifle. 
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.35,1:20:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我则装在箱子里回来{\r}\NI come home in a box.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.15,1:20:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你所做的对很多人很重要{\r}\NWhat you do is important to a lot of people.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.72,1:20:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不必了，好吗？听着，我放弃了{\r}\NForget it, will ya? Listen. I give up.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.65,1:20:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}废话说够了，我要走了，再见{\r}\NI'm gonna phone 'em in, okay? Enough bullshit. I'm outta here. See you, fellas.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.69,1:20:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我请你吃中饭{\r}\N- Buy you some lunch.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.86,1:20:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不能让你这么做{\r}\N- Can't let you do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.03,1:20:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如我不去上课，会有很多越南人{\r}\NListen, if I don't get to my class, there's gonna be a bunch of Vietnamese...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.46,1:20:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}说着残缺不全的英文{\r}\Nspeaking in short, choppy sentences.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.96,1:20:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们必需谈，马上谈{\r}\N- Look, we gotta talk. We gotta talk now.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.36,1:20:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不要现在，别这样！{\r}\N- Not now, man. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.23,1:20:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不相信你{\r}\NI can't believe you!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.24,1:20:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}什么？不好意思？{\r}\NWhat? That's it?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.34,1:20:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你把整个事情丢下了{\r}\NYou're gonna leave the whole fuckin' thing behind.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.57,1:21:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}把事情吊在半空，人们在依靠你{\r}\NYou're gonna leave everything fuckin' hanging. People are depending on you!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:01.48,1:21:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}艾伍，拜托{\r}\NEdward, please. 
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.61,1:21:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}一年中竟说了二个脏字{\r}\NThat's two nasty words in one year.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.98,1:21:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}原谅我！{\r}\N- Forgive me. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.18,1:21:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你要送我去学校？还是再买单车{\r}\NHey, you wanna give me a ride to school or am I gonna have to buy another bike?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.15,1:21:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}惹火我了{\r}\NYou're pissin' me off.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.50,1:21:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}为何道路阻塞了？  我看看{\r}\N- What the hell's the holdup? - Check it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.84,1:21:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你别说了好吗？你的口气渐渐像{\r}\NGarlick, will you cut it out? You're beginning to sound like a priest in a '40s movie.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.71,1:21:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}40年代电影中的爱尔兰神父{\r}\NGarlick, will you cut it out? You're beginning to sound like a priest in a '40s movie.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.85,1:21:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}当弟兄依靠你时我不会开除你{\r}\N[ lrish Accent ] We are not firing you when the boys are dependin' on you.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:48.92,1:21:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}各位  你在干什么？艾德{\r}\N- Gentlemen? - What are you doing, Ed?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.33,1:21:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}大伙！看看这位是谁？{\r}\NHey, guys. Guess who the hell I got in here.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.30,1:21:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别做这种狗屁事{\r}\N- Uh-oh. Don't do this shit. - [ Soldier ] Groucho Marx!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.17,1:21:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}克肯参议员{\r}\N- [ Soldier #2 ] Senator Dirksen.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.40,1:21:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}卷毛狗？{\r}\N- [ Soldier #3 ] Hey, Curly!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.97,1:22:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}再猜{\r}\N-Moe. -Come on, come on, come on. Guess again.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.60,1:22:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不必了，加利{\r}\N- Oh, bag it. Bag it, Garlick.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.24,1:22:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这里这位老兄{\r}\N- The fellow I got in here...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.41,1:22:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是唯一仅有的君子K你死定了{\r}\Nis the gentleman, the one and the only...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.38,1:22:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}广播界之王，艾德伦.康纳{\r}\N- You're a dead man. - king of the airwaves, Adrian Cronauer.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.95,1:22:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}彼得生，起来，康纳在这里{\r}\N[ Soldier ] Hey, Peterson, get up here, man. I think we got Cronauer here.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.05,1:22:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}康纳，说早安，越南{\r}\NHey, Cronauer, say "Good morning, Vietnam."
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.35,1:22:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}宽恕我吧，太热了{\r}\NOh, give me a break, man. It's too hot for radio shit, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.19,1:22:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}快...{\r}\N- Come on. - Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.23,1:22:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们怎知你是艾德伦.康纳？{\r}\N- How do we know it's Adrian Cronauer?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.33,1:22:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好{\r}\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.70,1:22:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我尽力而为{\r}\NI'll give her the best shot.
