Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.63,1:29:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I think to myself
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.83,1:29:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a wonderful world
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.67,1:29:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The colors of the rainbow
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.51,1:29:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So pretty in the sky
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.94,1:29:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are also on the faces
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.68,1:29:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of people going by
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.88,1:29:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see friends shakin' hands
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.92,1:29:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayin' How do you do
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.99,1:29:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're really saying I love you
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.50,1:29:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear babies crying
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.70,1:29:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I watch them grow
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.11,1:29:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll learn much more
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.21,1:29:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Than I'll ever know
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.24,1:29:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I think to myself
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.88,1:30:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a wonderful world
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.62,1:30:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I think to myself
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.23,1:30:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a wonderful world
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.04,1:30:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Oh, yeah - Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.51,1:30:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那是路易斯.B.阿母斯壮{\r}\NThat was Louis B. Armstrong,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.35,1:30:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}伟大的芸人{\r}\Nthe great Satchmo.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.65,1:30:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}想要采访战场上的大兵？{\r}\NWant to interview some G.I.s in the field, sir? 
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.22,1:30:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}将它在电台中播放{\r}\NAnd play those tapes on the radio?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.76,1:30:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}天才知道他们会说些什么{\r}\NGod only knows what they'd say, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.56,1:30:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这还牵扯到康纳，令人立刻起疑{\r}\NIt involves Cronauer, which makes me suspicious immediately.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.43,1:30:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}安勒，康纳一定会一起去{\r}\NAn Lac. And Cronauer would definitely be going along? 
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.17,1:30:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}等一下，长官{\r}\NHold on a minute, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.31,1:31:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}G-2 ，泰舍上等兵{\r}\NG-2, Corporal Tiser, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.01,1:31:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}等一下{\r}\NOne moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.48,1:31:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}1-A公路是唯一不平安的路{\r}\NRoute One-A, sir, is the only route to An Lac, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.52,1:31:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那条路有安全警戒吗？{\r}\NDoes that road have a secure status?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.15,1:31:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没有，那条路在越共手中{\r}\NNo, sir, it does not. That road is Victor Charlie, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.46,1:31:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那绝对不是友善的地区了{\r}\N- It is definitely not a friendly area.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.33,1:31:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不是，长官，不是{\r}\N- Negative, sir. It is not.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:21.23,1:31:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}已经失守了48小时{\r}\NIt is hazardous and, uh, has been for about 48 hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.07,1:31:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}火力强大及非常不安全{\r}\NHeavily fortified and considered very unsafe, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.24,1:31:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谢谢你  （越共在窃听）{\r}\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.54,1:31:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}长官，建议核准24小时通行证{\r}\NSir, I recommend we issue a 24-hour pass.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.32,1:31:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}“1-A小径已落入越共手中”{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.56,1:31:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}木椅就是在这里生长的{\r}\NSo this is the country where they grow rattan love seats.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.83,1:31:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}天呀，好热{\r}\N- [ Chuckles ] - God, is it hot.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.93,1:32:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好个国家！热，羞辱，恐怖份子{\r}\NWhat a country. Heat, humidity, terrorism.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.34,1:32:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但仍比夏天的纽约要好{\r}\NStill, it's better than New Y ork in the summer.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.64,1:32:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}二位，咳嗽药的生意如何？{\r}\NHey, fellas, how's the cough drop business?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.68,1:32:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}自从长泰后就没经过检查哨了{\r}\NYou know, we haven't passed too many checkpoints since Chon Thanh.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.02,1:32:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你为何把越南城镇想成墨式餐厅{\r}\NWhy do you make every Vietnamese town sound like a Mexican restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.86,1:32:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}英国今天扣留罗德西亚油轮关税{\r}\NBritain imposed an oil embargo on Rhodesia today...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.36,1:32:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}除非该国不庆祝独立纪念日{\r}\Nafter that country's unilateral declaration of independence.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.30,1:32:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}干比亚，新加坡，马尔帝群岛{\r}\NGambia, Singapore and the Maldive lslands j
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.17,1:32:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}加入了联合国{\r}\Noin the United Nations.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.87,1:32:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}金帝甘已成为比丘旺岛首任首相{\r}\NSertse Khama becomes the first premier of Bechuanaland.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.77,1:32:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}体育新闻方面...{\r}\NIn sports, all-star rookie Pete Rose's three hits--
Dialogue: 0,1:32:40.41,1:32:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你想在这一切之后做什么？艾德{\r}\NWhat do you think you'll do after all this, Ed?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:42.48,1:32:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}当你退伍后{\r}\NWhen you get out of the army?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.81,1:32:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我学的已足够在电台工作了{\r}\NI think I learned enough about radio stations--
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.85,1:32:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我是说也许能在家乡电台工作{\r}\NI mean, maybe I can work in a station back home or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.48,1:32:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}真的？拿点本事出来{\r}\NReally? Give me your best shot. Lay somethin' on me.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.98,1:32:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}试一下，试一下{\r}\NGive it a go. Give it a go.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.32,1:32:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这是艾迪.加利由AFRS报导{\r}\NThis is Eddie Garlick comin' to you live from AFRS, Armed Forces Radio Saigon.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.42,1:32:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}玩够了，来点真本事{\r}\NNow funkify it. Give me some real funk.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.23,1:33:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}说出来，艾伍{\r}\NGive it to me, Edward.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.09,1:33:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这是艾迪加利{\r}\N- This is Eddie Garlick, com-- - Heh!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.60,1:33:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}早安，越南{\r}\NGood morning, Vietnam!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.78,1:33:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你们是收听AFRS的艾迪克尔{\r}\NYou're listening to Eddie Kirk on AFRS. 
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.72,1:33:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我有个特殊的...{\r}\NI have a big special--
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.31,1:33:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,..for, but we need to hear your requests. - [ Speaking Vietnamese ]
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.54,1:33:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So send in your postcards to Eddie Kirk, right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.72,1:34:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你被找到了{\r}\NYou fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.32,1:34:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你怎样了？{\r}\N How you are?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.22,1:34:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}带你回家{\r}\NTake you home.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.99,1:34:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你出来{\r}\NYou come out.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.56,1:34:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没问题，带你回家 现在和越共一起很平安{\r}\NNo problem. Take you home. Safe now from V.C.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.81,1:34:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这是马帝李在康纳的控制中心{\r}\NHi. This is Marty Lee Dreiwitz at Cronauer Control Center.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.28,1:34:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}康纳暂时出任务，我替补他{\r}\NAdrian Cronauer is on temporary assignment,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.59,1:34:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}希望他今早会回来{\r}\Nand I'll be filling in until he arrives, hopefully sometime this morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.52,1:34:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}现在放艾德伦的歌{\r}\NRight now, let's play a song
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.73,1:34:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}也是他最喜欢的歌之一{\r}\Nfrom Adrian's own play list, one of A.C.'s favorites.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.07,1:34:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}“两名美国军人K”{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:50.77,1:34:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}今天的节目既有趣K{\r}\NIt's going to be an exciting day
Dialogue: 0,1:34:52.87,1:34:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}又能学到不少东西{\r}\Nof listening and learning,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:54.61,1:34:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}敬请注意收听{\r}\Nso please, tune in.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.48,1:35:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Sukiyaki," "Volare," "The Portuguese Washerwoman"...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.82,1:35:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and "Third Man Theme" on the Kirk lnternational--
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.79,1:35:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}（越南语）{\r}\N- Baby, please don't go - [ Speaking Vietnamese ]
Dialogue: 0,1:35:12.49,1:35:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know I love you so Baby, please don't go
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.80,1:35:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Baby, I'm done gone Baby, I'm done gone - Hold it, hold it, hold it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.94,1:35:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}（越南语）{\r}\N[ Speaking Vietnamese ]
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.31,1:35:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}什么事？{\r}\N- What's up?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.18,1:35:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想要找康纳{\r}\N- I try to find Cronow.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.28,1:35:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他没去上课{\r}\NHe don't show up in class.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.68,1:35:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他今天也没来上班{\r}\NHe didn't show up for work today either.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.78,1:35:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你知道这件事吗？{\r}\N You know anything about this?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.28,1:35:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}听着，我们是来为你们国家打仗{\r}\NListen, jerkoff! We're here fighting for your country!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.85,1:35:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}康纳去那里了？{\r}\N- Now where did Cronauer go? - An Lac.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.22,1:35:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}安勒，他说去安勒{\r}\N- His pass say "An Lac."
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.72,1:35:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}安勒？{\r}\N- An Lac?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.02,1:35:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}妈的{\r}\N Shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.21,1:35:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你没事吗？{\r}\N- [ Cronauer ] You okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.97,1:36:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是{\r}\N- [ Garlick ] Yeah. Yeah. 
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.14,1:36:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你没事吗？{\r}\NYou okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.81,1:36:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不{\r}\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:05.68,1:36:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}走，我们会办到的{\r}\NCome on, pal. We'll make it.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:07.65,1:36:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我有预感{\r}\N- I have a hunch. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:12.49,1:36:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}越共，他妈的越共{\r}\N- V.C. The fuckin' V.C.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.22,1:36:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}说些我不知道的事，好吗？{\r}\N- Tell me somethin' I don't know, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:31.57,1:36:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你想我们走多远了？{\r}\NHow far you think we've gone?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:33.74,1:36:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}10 ， 15哩{\r}\NTen, fifteen miles.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:36.64,1:36:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你想我们到高棉了吗？{\r}\NThink we've reached Cambodia yet?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.71,1:36:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在这种地方你怎能打仗？{\r}\NHow can you fight a war in this shit?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.88,1:36:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不知他们在那里{\r}\NI don't know where they are.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.95,1:36:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我连自己在哪也不知道{\r}\NI don't even know where I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:45.39,1:36:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}什么也看不见{\r}\NCan't see dick.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.59,1:36:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好像和瞎子雷查尔斯一起打猎{\r}\NLike hunting with Ray Charles.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.33,1:36:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没问题{\r}\N[ Tuan ] It okay! 
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.16,1:36:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你们可以出来了{\r}\NYou can come out now.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:57.86,1:37:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}听见了吗？不和我说话我找不到{\r}\NIf you here, I cannot find you unless you talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:01.33,1:37:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}待在这里太危险了{\r}\NIt's too dangerous staying here.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.44,1:37:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你不相信是我吗？{\r}\NYou don't believe it's me?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:05.61,1:37:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好，给他一记{\r}\NOkay. Flip them the bird!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.88,1:37:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}泛？{\r}\N- Tuan?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:11.55,1:37:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你在这里呀，康纳{\r}\N- Hey, there you are, Cronauer.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.75,1:37:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你如何找到我们的？聪明小子{\r}\NHow the helI'd you find us, Sparky?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.75,1:37:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你的吉普车{\r}\NYour Jeep.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.02,1:37:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们显然不是在高棉{\r}\NWe're obviously not in Cambodia.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.32,1:37:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}再试试{\r}\N- [ Starter Cranking ] - [ Garlick ] Try it again.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:29.43,1:37:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}再一次{\r}\N- [ Garlick ] One more time. - [ Starter Cranking ]
Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.80,1:37:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}天杀的{\r}\NGoddamn it. 
Dialogue: 0,1:37:36.04,1:37:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们的吉普被炸了，他的发不动{\r}\NOur Jeep gets blown off the road, and his van won't start.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.94,1:37:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}真棒{\r}\N- That's great. 
Dialogue: 0,1:37:40.64,1:37:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你可知我们为何会再走回来吗？{\r}\NYou know why we ended up in the same place.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.48,1:37:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}为什么？{\r}\N- Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.21,1:37:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你向右跛使我们绕圈子{\r}\NYour limp pulled us to the right. We were going around in circles.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.71,1:37:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}紧跟我走，我不想再绕圈子了{\r}\NStick with me. I don't want to go around again.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.95,1:37:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不再是在堪萨斯了{\r}\N[ Cronauer ] We're not in Kansas anymore, Toto.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.46,1:38:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}听！{\r}\N- Listen. - [ Helicopter Blades Whirring ]
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.07,1:38:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在那边{\r}\NSomewhere over there.
