Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.17,1:39:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}闷热中的卫生到此为止，明天...{\r}\NThat's it for "Hygiene in the Heat." Tomorrow we'll-- That's it for "Hygiene in the Heat." Tomorrow we'll--
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.87,1:39:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}欢迎你回来{\r}\N- Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.20,1:39:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谢谢你，士官长，我想念你{\r}\N- Thank you, Sergeant. I've missed you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.78,1:39:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我通知你要离开此了{\r}\NI'm informing you that you're outta here.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:23.84,1:39:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我要你收拾好行李，明天下午走{\r}\NI want your bags packed and ready to go tomorrow afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:26.48,1:39:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你没有这权力，我会向上级报告{\r}\N[ Laughs ] You don't have the power. I'll take this right to the authorities.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:29.78,1:39:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我就是上级，你这低能儿{\r}\NI am the authorities, you moron.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:35.66,1:39:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我抓到你的弱点了，康纳{\r}\NOh, I got your pansy ass in a sling now, Cronauer.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.46,1:39:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谁是泛？{\r}\NWho's Tuan? 
Dialogue: 0,1:39:40.96,1:39:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}由安勒接你们回来的人报告说{\r}\NThe guys who flew you in from An Lac...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.80,1:39:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他们载了你和加利及位越南少年{\r}\Nradioed they'd picked up a young South Vietnamese boy with you and Garlick.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:45.10,1:39:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这位越南少年是谁？{\r}\NWho is this South Vietnamese boy?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.10,1:39:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我班上的一位朋友，冒险去救我{\r}\N- He's a friend from my class who risked his ass to save my life. - A "friend"?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.40,1:39:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}朋友？你朋友是位越共恐怖份子{\r}\N- Your friend is a V.C. terrorist. - [ Laughs ]
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.71,1:39:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对，我母亲是狼人{\r}\NYeah, and my mother's a werewolf, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:55.64,1:39:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}也是泛德多一份子{\r}\NTuan is also known as Phan Duc Tho.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.08,1:40:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}越南警方因几起爆炸案而通缉他{\r}\NHe's currently wanted by the South Vietnamese police... in connection with several bombings in the area,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.72,1:40:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}包括吉米的店{\r}\Nincluding the one at Jimmy Wah's.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.65,1:40:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你对这件意外一定很熟{\r}\NSurely you're familiar with that incident.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.12,1:40:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你是否奇怪一位越南少年{\r}\NDid you ever wonder how a young South Vietnamese boy...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.46,1:40:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}怎能进出越共占领的地区{\r}\Ngets into and out of V.C.-held territory?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.73,1:40:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那边很危险，事情突如其来{\r}\NIt's dangerous out there. Things just jump out at you.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.60,1:40:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}而这男孩却能毫无损伤的进出{\r}\NAnd yet this boy can get in and out without a scratch.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.87,1:40:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}吉米的店呢？{\r}\NAnd what about Jimmy Wah's? Didn't you ever wonder why you were pulled out...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.44,1:40:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你不奇怪为何你在爆炸前被拉走{\r}\Njust moments before the whole place blew up?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:28.04,1:40:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}或是你平常不太爱追根究底{\r}\NOr are you normally not that inquisitive?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.81,1:40:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}泛德多的朋友{\r}\NFriends of Phan Duc Tho.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.42,1:40:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这三位在这照片拍完后不久{\r}\NThese three were executed shortly
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.39,1:40:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}就被枪杀了{\r}\Nafter this photo was taken.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.23,1:40:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你的朋友是下一位{\r}\NYour friend is next.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.40,1:40:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不期望对这件事你会赞成我{\r}\NI don't recommend that you tangle with me on this one, Airman.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.90,1:40:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}高阶军官会同情和恐怖份子{\r}\NThere's not too many high-ranking officers would be sympathetic...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:54.83,1:40:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}挂勾的军可不会多{\r}\Nto a serviceman with links to terrorists.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.97,1:40:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}军方对这种事很不赞同{\r}\NThe army is kind of quirky that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:59.97,1:41:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对于背叛美国的罪刑是要{\r}\NA conviction on the charge of treason against the United States...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.51,1:41:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}二眼翻白的，如你明白我的意思{\r}\Ncarries with it some penalties kind of on the stiff side, if you know what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:06.75,1:41:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我已安排好荣誉退伍{\r}\NI have arranged for an honorable discharge, provided
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.32,1:41:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}使你不发生事情而离去{\r}\Nyou leave without incident.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:11.85,1:41:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}立正{\r}\N- Ten hut.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:12.92,1:41:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}稍息{\r}\N- At ease.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:18.69,1:41:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我对这件事很抱歉{\r}\NCronauer, I'm sorry as hell about this thing. 
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.63,1:41:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}天杀的，我喜欢你，孩子{\r}\NGoddamn it, I like you, son.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.26,1:41:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我喜欢你做的事{\r}\NI like what you do.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:23.80,1:41:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}最重要的是我喜欢你为弟兄做的{\r}\N Most of all, I like what you've done for the men.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.87,1:41:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但事实就是事实{\r}\NBut facts are facts.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:29.00,1:41:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这有可能使军方难堪 这次我不担保你了{\r}\NThis could give the army a black eye. I'm not gonna cover for you this time, son.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:35.34,1:41:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}长官？{\r}\NSir?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.78,1:41:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}节目怎么办？{\r}\NWhat about the show?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:39.91,1:41:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们会处理它{\r}\NWe'll handle it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:42.75,1:41:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}抱歉，孩子{\r}\NI'm sorry, son.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.26,1:41:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你为何要这么做？{\r}\NWhy'd you do this?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:53.09,1:41:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不喜欢你的风格{\r}\NI don't like your style, 
Dialogue: 0,1:41:54.73,1:41:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你的政治或你的幽默{\r}\Nyour politics or your sense of humor.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:57.13,1:41:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不喜欢你说的话或说法{\r}\NI don't like what you say or how you say it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:59.90,1:42:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}从现在起，在越南作战的人{\r}\NFrom now on, the fighting men of Vietnam will hear exactly
Dialogue: 0,1:42:01.53,1:42:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}将会听到他们该听到的{\r}\Nwhat they're supposed to hear.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:03.57,1:42:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你明天1830时搭DC-8机{\r}\NYou're on a DC-8 from Tan Son Nhut airport tomorrow at 1830 hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:07.77,1:42:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我建议你安静点收拾行李{\r}\NI recommend you pack quietly.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.81,1:42:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我对你只有这些话，空军{\r}\NThat's all I have for you, Airman.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:24.26,1:42:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你知道吗？{\r}\NYou know,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:26.46,1:42:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你比白人历史上最需要{\r}\Nyou're in more dire need of a blow job
Dialogue: 0,1:42:28.43,1:42:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}口交的人还悲惨{\r}\Nthan any white man in history.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:36.04,1:42:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你来了，迪克，先别走{\r}\NWhoa there, Dick. Put the brakes on.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:38.20,1:42:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我要等空军走了再跟你谈谈{\r}\NI wanted to wait 'til the airman left to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.04,1:42:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}迪克，我要把你调走{\r}\NUh, Dick, I'm transferring you.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.74,1:42:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}调我走？长官{\r}\N- Transferring me, sir? - Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:46.18,1:42:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}去那里？长官{\r}\N- Where to, sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:48.18,1:42:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你去关岛{\r}\N- You're going to Guam.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.55,1:42:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}关岛？那里什么事也没有{\r}\NGuam, sir! There's nothin' goin' on in Guam!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:51.45,1:42:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}为何选关岛？{\r}\N Why Guam?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.69,1:42:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}迪克，我为何掩饰了很多次{\r}\NDick, I've covered for you a lot of times 
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.55,1:42:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}因我认为你有点疯疯颠颠{\r}\N'cause I thought you was a little crazy.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.82,1:42:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但你不是疯颠，你是恶毒{\r}\NBut you're not crazy. You're mean.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:59.89,1:43:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}而这只是电台而已{\r}\NAnd this is just radio.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.90,1:43:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}比白人历史上{\r}\NMore dire need of a blow job
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.67,1:43:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}更需要口交的还悲惨{\r}\N than any white man in history.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:14.71,1:43:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这真好笑{\r}\N That's funny.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:26.62,1:43:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}几时教我们打垒球？老师...{\r}\NHey, Teacher! When are you gonna teach us softball?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:30.19,1:43:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我要和你谈谈{\r}\NListen, I gotta talk to you. Now! Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.72,1:43:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}现在，来{\r}\N- Mr. Cronauer, I must talk to you. - Oh, Minh, not now.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:35.03,1:43:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你必需告诉我你弟弟在那里{\r}\N- Listen, you gotta tell me where your brother is. - Don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:36.53,1:43:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不知道 听着，他生命有危险{\r}\NListen, his life is in danger.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:39.23,1:43:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你必需告诉我他在那里{\r}\NYou gotta tell me where the hell he is.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:40.97,1:43:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不，我不...  胡说{\r}\N- No, I don't-- - Bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:43.00,1:43:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}听着，别再玩把戏了，好吗？{\r}\NListen. No more games, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.27,1:43:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}军方知道你弟弟的事{\r}\NThe army knows about your brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:47.94,1:43:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}因我和他的关系而必需离开了{\r}\NI have to leave the country because of my association with him.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.98,1:43:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他们有他的照片{\r}\NThey have pictures of him.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:52.58,1:43:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}找到他的话会杀了他{\r}\NIf they find him, they will shoot him.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:54.85,1:43:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如你还想要有位弟弟就带我去{\r}\NIf you want to continue to have a brother, you take me to him now!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:10.12,1:45:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}泛德多{\r}\NPhan Duc Tho!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:16.40,1:45:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}回来{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:19.36,1:46:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}爆炸的事我知道了，聪明小子{\r}\NKnow about the bombings, Sparky.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:22.86,1:46:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}难怪你能大命不死{\r}\NNo wonder you hauled ass.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.17,1:46:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你是我的朋友{\r}\NYou were my friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:36.74,1:46:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我信任你{\r}\NI trusted you.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:42.52,1:46:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你听见了吗？{\r}\N[ Shouting ] You hear me?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.45,1:46:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你是位天真的人，康纳{\r}\N[ Tuan ] You naive man, Cronauer.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:47.42,1:46:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你选了愚笨的一国{\r}\NYou take a stupid side.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:49.46,1:46:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}现在你则要走了{\r}\NNow you have to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:51.12,1:46:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这样也好{\r}\NIt's better off.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:52.59,1:46:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}重点不在此{\r}\NThat's not the fucking point!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:56.33,1:46:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你了解吗？{\r}\NUnderstand me?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:58.77,1:47:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我为了你能进那酒吧而打架{\r}\NI fought to get you into that bar...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.87,1:47:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你却把那酒吧给炸了{\r}\Nand then you blow the fuckin' place up!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:05.07,1:47:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}听着，我付出了友谊和信任给你{\r}\NListen. I gave you my friendship and my trust...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:11.04,1:47:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}现在他们告诉我{\r}\Nand now they tell me that my best friend is the goddamn enemy!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:12.05,1:47:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我最好的朋友是敌人 敌人？ 什么才是敌人？{\r}\NEnemy? What is enemy?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:18.58,1:47:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你们离家数千哩来此杀我们的人{\r}\NYou killing my own people so many miles from your home.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:21.62,1:47:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们不是敌人，你们才是敌人{\r}\NWe not the enemy. You the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:25.16,1:47:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你利用我而杀害二个人{\r}\NYou used me to kill two people.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.39,1:47:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}二个人死于那酒吧里{\r}\NTwo people died in that fuckin' bar.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:29.46,1:47:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有什么了不起{\r}\NBig fucking deal!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:32.30,1:47:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我母亲死了{\r}\NMy mother is dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:34.93,1:47:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我另一位哥哥也是，才29岁{\r}\NAnd my older brother, who be 29 years old,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:37.77,1:47:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他也死了{\r}\Nhe dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:39.44,1:47:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}被美国人开枪打死{\r}\NShot by Americans.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:42.68,1:47:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我的邻居死了{\r}\NMy neighbor, dead. His wife, dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:45.18,1:47:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他太太死了，为什么？{\r}\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:48.88,1:47:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}因为我们在他们眼中不是人类{\r}\NBecause we're not human to them.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:51.38,1:47:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们只是小越南人{\r}\NWe're only little Vietnamese.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:57.46,1:48:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}而我却笨到去安勒救你一命{\r}\NAnd I'm stupid enough to save your bullshit life at An Lac.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:08.17,1:48:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}等等{\r}\NWait.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:10.30,1:48:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们是来帮助这个国家的{\r}\NWe're here to help this country.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:12.91,1:48:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你跑去那里了{\r}\NWhere the fuck you goin'?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:23.92,1:48:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不可置信{\r}\NIt's unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:26.42,1:48:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在西贡只待了5个月{\r}\NFive months in Saigon...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:29.19,1:48:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我最好的朋友竟是越共{\r}\Nand my best friend turns out to be a V.C.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:32.86,1:48:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这在履历上将不太好看{\r}\NThis will not look good on a resume!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:51.14,1:48:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}介意我来开车吗？  请便{\r}\N- You guys mind if I drive? - Be my guest.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:08.90,1:49:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}只是一个简单的规矩{\r}\NIt's a simple rule.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:10.20,1:49:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如马达有声音就表示已发动了{\r}\NIf the engine's humming, it's already started.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:13.17,1:49:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}绝不会令你失望{\r}\NNever fails. 
Dialogue: 0,1:49:14.23,1:49:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你们介意我们先去一下别处吗？{\r}\NYou guys mind if we make a little unscheduled stop?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:16.20,1:49:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我有些事要办{\r}\N- I got something I gotta do.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.54,1:49:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如你想藉故拖延登机时间{\r}\N- If you attempt to deviate from the aforeplanned schedule,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:20.01,1:49:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}记住你已是被捕的人{\r}\Nyou're under arrest, Cronauer.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:22.04,1:49:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好，各位，开始赛球{\r}\N- [ Chattering ] - Okay, everybody, let's play ball!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.98,1:49:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好，开始{\r}\NGo into conference. That point. That fence. - Okay, here we go. - Go, batter. Go, batter.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:31.18,1:49:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Headin' north!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:33.52,1:49:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这是二垒打或是台克利酒？{\r}\NLet's go! Was it a double or a daiquiri?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:36.36,1:49:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute. [ Muttering ] All right!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:39.33,1:49:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:42.36,1:49:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}开个会，暂停{\r}\N- [ Mutters ] - [ Cronauer ] Whoa. A little conference.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:46.33,1:49:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}康纳，这不是真的棒球{\r}\N- Time out, everyone. - This not like a real baseball.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:47.90,1:49:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}要比这个要小，要硬{\r}\NIt much smaller and harder than... than this one.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:51.90,1:49:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你说对了，对不起，经费不够{\r}\NYou got me there, Wilk, because-- I'm sorry. We have no budget, you see.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:55.31,1:49:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我还要去坐飞机，只有尽其所用{\r}\NAnd I gotta get on a plane, and we have to do with what we can.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:58.24,1:50:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}手给我，谢谢  还是谢谢你{\r}\N- Give me your hand. Thank you. - Thank you all the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:01.08,1:50:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}还是谢谢你{\r}\N- Thank you all the same, and--
Dialogue: 0,1:50:03.12,1:50:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你要把球拿去吗？  不{\r}\NYou wanna take the ball? - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:05.28,1:50:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好，我们还要玩，你是投手{\r}\NOkay. We gotta play, Wilk. You're pitchin'.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:07.65,1:50:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我要把球放回原来的地方 好{\r}\NI want to turn in the ball to the-- see, the original place.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:10.66,1:50:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们再拿一个球，这个比较好{\r}\N- Okay. Let's take one more ball here. This one's a better one. - No, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:12.86,1:50:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不，不是真的{\r}\N- Not that one? 
Dialogue: 0,1:50:14.59,1:50:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们没有真的球{\r}\NWe haven't got a real baseball, Wilk. - No need.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:15.76,1:50:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}忍耐点，好吗？  好{\r}\N- Bear with me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:17.26,1:50:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}钱不够{\r}\NWe haven't got the money, pal. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:19.20,1:50:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这个可以吗？{\r}\N- Okay? Is that one okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:20.20,1:50:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这是很好的替代品{\r}\N- Anyway. I accept that this is a very good substitute.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:22.24,1:50:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好，就用替代品来玩，好吗？{\r}\N- Okay. Let's just play with the substitute then, okay? - Mmm-hmm. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:24.87,1:50:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好，一言为定{\r}\N- Okay. It's a deal? Okay. - This is a deal. This a deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:28.17,1:50:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那就拿着球，我会给你钱{\r}\NTake the ball with you, then, Wilk. I'll give you money if you take the ball.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:31.01,1:50:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不   不？{\r}\N- No. 
Dialogue: 0,1:50:31.94,1:50:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对不起   好{\r}\NI'm sorry. - No? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:33.78,1:50:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我没有钱{\r}\N- I'm-I'm-- I've no money. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:34.88,1:50:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这里有心理医生吗？{\r}\N- Is there a psychiatrist here?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:45.06,1:50:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Go! Run, run, run!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:50.46,1:50:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}球没有碰他之前他还没有出局{\r}\NHe's not out 'til you have both hands on the ball!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:52.57,1:50:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对了，眼睛看着水果{\r}\N[ Cronauer ] Keep your eye on the fruit. That's it. Eye on the fruit. Okay, on the fruit, on the fruit.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:58.30,1:51:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好呀！快跑{\r}\NGo, go! Run, Minh! Run!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:00.37,1:51:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Minh!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:02.48,1:51:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Keep go-- Keep going!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:06.05,1:51:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}她回家去了{\r}\N- She's actually goin' home. - Well, I'm goin' out West where I belong
Dialogue: 0,1:51:10.78,1:51:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it. We'll all change sides.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:13.45,1:51:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the days are short and the nights are long
Dialogue: 0,1:51:16.76,1:51:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yes, Wilkie! - Well, they walk and I walk
Dialogue: 0,1:51:21.19,1:51:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你有垒包要踏{\r}\N- They twist and I'll twist - Hey, Wilk, you got a base.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:24.10,1:51:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They shimmy and I'll shimmy They fly and I'll fly
Dialogue: 0,1:51:28.94,1:51:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they're out there a-havin' fun
Dialogue: 0,1:51:32.04,1:51:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that warm California sun
Dialogue: 0,1:51:34.91,1:51:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm goin' out West out on the coast
Dialogue: 0,1:51:40.01,1:51:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the California girls are really the most
Dialogue: 0,1:51:45.52,1:51:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where they walk and I'll walk
Dialogue: 0,1:51:47.85,1:51:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They twist and I'll twist
Dialogue: 0,1:51:50.79,1:51:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They shimmy and I'll shimmy
Dialogue: 0,1:51:54.43,1:51:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They fly and I'll fly
Dialogue: 0,1:51:57.16,1:51:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they're out there havin' fun
Dialogue: 0,1:51:59.93,1:52:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that warm California sun
Dialogue: 0,1:52:08.61,1:52:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y eah, me too. Hey, hey. Oh, hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:11.48,1:52:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}当你看来像圣人葛莱亚时{\r}\NWhen you look like Goliath, so might you...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:14.95,1:52:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你就可能要小心大卫了{\r}\N- [ Cronauer ] You take care. - beware of, of some David. We had a great day. [ Speaking Vietnamese ]
Dialogue: 0,1:52:20.45,1:52:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谢谢{\r}\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:24.19,1:52:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}康纳先生，我们谢谢你{\r}\NWell, Mr. Cronauer, we, we thank you for
Dialogue: 0,1:52:26.86,1:52:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好心的教导我们打垒球{\r}\Nyour fine teaching about softball,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:28.76,1:52:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们从你这里学了很多东西{\r}\Nand we have learned a lot from you
Dialogue: 0,1:52:30.96,1:52:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们祝你好运并成功{\r}\Nand we wish you good luck and success.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:33.43,1:52:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谢谢{\r}\N- Thank you, Wilkie. Thank you. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:35.87,1:52:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谢谢{\r}\N- Thank you. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:43.34,1:52:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}给我一分钟{\r}\N- [ M.P. ] You guys ready to go? - Can you give me a minute?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:50.55,1:52:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他要对全国说再见{\r}\NMan, he's gonna say good-bye to the whole goddamn country now.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:03.16,1:53:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我要来说再见{\r}\NI want to say good-bye
Dialogue: 0,1:53:05.36,1:53:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在你走之前{\r}\Nbefore you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:09.07,1:53:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}告诉你{\r}\NTo tell you...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:11.44,1:53:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谢谢你如此好心{\r}\Nthank you for being so kind.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:15.64,1:53:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你所想要的很多事并没有发生{\r}\NSo many things not happen the way you want it.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:21.95,1:53:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你是位非常好的人{\r}\NYou so good person,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:25.02,1:53:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但我不能与你一起{\r}\Nbut I could not with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:29.29,1:53:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们太不相同了{\r}\NWe are so different.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:31.96,1:53:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我说蕃茄，你说...{\r}\NI say "tomato." You say "xioh phoung."
Dialogue: 0,1:53:56.45,1:53:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}再见{\r}\N[ Voice Cracking ] See you.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:07.86,1:54:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}想像力太棒了{\r}\N- Staggers the imagination.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:10.26,1:54:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}使我很别致，对不？{\r}\N- Makes me unique, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:11.53,1:54:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}加三级{\r}\NWhat a plus.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:14.13,1:54:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flip them the bird!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:26.55,1:54:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Left, right, left!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:38.49,1:54:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Left, right!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:00.41,1:55:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[ Together ] Three, four!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:07.85,1:55:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Left, left! Left, right, left!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:10.92,1:55:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Left, left! Left, right, left!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:16.93,1:55:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- [ Shouting ] - Left, left! Left, right, left!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:40.49,1:55:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}很荣幸认识你，长官{\r}\NIt was a pleasure making your acquaintance, sir. 
Dialogue: 0,1:55:42.82,1:55:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谢谢{\r}\NThanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:44.49,1:55:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}少来了，加利，我们阶级相同{\r}\NCut that out, Garlick. We're the same rank.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:47.16,1:55:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没有你我该怎么办？{\r}\NWhat will I do without you, sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:49.16,1:55:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你继续下去，勇士{\r}\N- Well, you carry on, Montesque. - Carry on, Montesque.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:51.90,1:55:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你继续下去，勇士{\r}\NCarry on. I like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:54.23,1:55:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我喜欢，使我觉得像英国人{\r}\NIt makes me feel, uh, British or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:58.34,1:56:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我有个东西给你{\r}\NI've got something here for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:00.74,1:56:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}播放这个{\r}\NI want you to play this.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:02.31,1:56:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是对留下的人说再见{\r}\N It says good-bye to everybody stayin' behind.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:04.08,1:56:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我会好好处理{\r}\N- I'll take care of it pronto, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:05.71,1:56:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有可能惹上麻烦{\r}\N- You could get in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:07.65,1:56:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我已申请改名字了{\r}\NI requisitioned for a name change.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:09.18,1:56:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}麻烦是我中间的名字{\r}\NTrouble is my new middle name.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:14.59,1:56:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我现在要给你老式的打一下肩膀{\r}\NI'll give you the old chuck on the shoulder now.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:17.89,1:56:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这是个笨举动，对不？{\r}\NIt's a stupid thing to do, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:21.46,1:56:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你多保重{\r}\NYou take care.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:23.90,1:56:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}艾德{\r}\NEd, your fly's open.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:25.56,1:56:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你裤挡没关，不必看了{\r}\NMade you look.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:52.09,1:56:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}早安，越南{\r}\NGo-oo-ood morning, Vietnam!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:55.90,1:56:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这是艾迪加利{\r}\NThis is Eddie Garlick
Dialogue: 0,1:56:56.83,1:56:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}由AFRS为你实况播报{\r}\Ncoming to you live from AFRS,
Dialogue: 0,1:56:59.23,1:57:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}西贡美军电台{\r}\NArmed Forces Radio Saigon.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:01.37,1:57:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}现在西贡时间是1629时{\r}\NIt's 1629 hours here in Saigon,
Dialogue: 0,1:57:03.84,1:57:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}今天空军艾德伦.康纳回家了{\r}\Nand Airman Adrian Cronauer is going home today.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:05.97,1:57:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但他对那些在战场上流汗的弟兄{\r}\NBut he left a farewell message for all you guys out there
Dialogue: 0,1:57:08.17,1:57:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}留下了道别讯息{\r}\Nsweating it out in the fields.
